s%20(R).%3Cp%3ELumin%20Fitness%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fitness%20studio%20was%20founded%20by%20Brandon%20Bean%2C%20former%20CEO%20of%20gym%20franchise%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolds-gym-bankruptcy-coronavirus-pandemic-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGold's%20Gym%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Omeed%20Shams%2C%20who%20previously%20founded%20a%20mixed-reality%20gaming%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20Lumin%20Fitness%20studio%20opened%20last%20September%20in%20Irving%2C%20Texas.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lumin%20fitness%20studio%20equipment%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3e78e6fcb546d2d4d39c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20collection%20of%20dumbells%2C%20resistance%20bands%2C%20and%20other%20gym%20equipment%20at%20Lumin%20Fitness.%3Cp%3ELumin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20studio%20includes%20a%20range%20of%20equipment%20such%20as%20dumbbells%2C%20kettlebells%2C%20slam%20balls%2C%20resistance%20bands%2C%20and%20jump%20ropes%2C%20Lumin%20Fitness%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Bikes%20are%20also%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20AI%20studio%20features%20interactive%2C%20wall-to-wall%20LED%20displays%20embedded%20with%20motion%20sensors%20that%20track%20gymgoers'%20movements.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lumin%20fitness%20studio%20equipment%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3e9536fcb546d2d4d3a57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20row%20of%20custom%20gym%20equipment%20at%20Lumin%20designed%20with%20AI%20capabilities.%20%3Cp%3ELumin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20sensor%20technology%2C%20the%20studio%20automatically%20checks%20members%20in%2C%20directs%20them%20to%20their%20dedicated%20station%2C%20and%20guides%20them%20through%20their%20workout%20in%20a%20safe%20manner%2C%20Lumin%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EExercisers%20can%20select%20their%20AI%20trainer%20through%20Lumin's%20smartphone%20app.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223970%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20exercising%20at%20lumin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3e9057a3d27148878c2fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224176%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAttendees%20work%20out%20by%20following%20instructions%20from%20the%20AI%20trainer%20through%20their%20headphones.%20%3Cp%3ELumin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20trainer%20guides%20gymgoers%20through%20a%20workout%20in%20real%20time%20through%20their%20headphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20algorithms%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20the%20sensors%20count%20an%20exerciser's%20every%20rep%2C%20track%20how%20they%20use%20their%20equipment%2C%20and%20monitor%20their%20movements%20without%20them%20needing%20to%20wear%20a%20piece%20of%20technology%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20can%20then%20simultaneously%20analyze%20the%20collected%20data%20and%20give%20exercisers%20real-time%20feedback%20on%20their%20form%2C%20technique%2C%20and%20range%20of%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAttendees%20can%20choose%20between%20a%2040-minute%20solo%20class%20or%20a%20group%20class%20led%20by%20AI.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221078%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20lifting%20dumbells%20at%20lumin%20fitness%20studio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3e9fa6fcb546d2d4d3aa1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221092%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWomen%20at%20a%20group%20class%20at%20a%20Lumin%20Fitness%20studio.%3Cp%3ELumin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESolo%20classes%20generate%20an%20exercise%20plan%20based%20on%20the%20attendee's%20specific%20fitness%20goals%20%E2%80%94%20like%20growing%20certain%20muscle%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGroup%20classes%20involve%20a%20high-intensity%20functional%20training%20workout%20designed%20to%20build%20aerobic%2C%20muscular%2C%20and%20motor%20strength%20and%20improve%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20studio's%20AI%20technology%20tracks%20members'%20progress%20from%20one%20class%20to%20the%20next%20by%20remembering%20personal%20workout%20records.%20The%20data%20are%20used%20to%20recommend%20appropriate%20equipment%20and%20weights%20and%20to%20suggest%20improvements%20like%20form%20correction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EExercisers%20can%20rack%20up%20points%20for%20completing%20workouts%20which%20can%20be%20exchanged%20for%20digital%20and%20physical%20rewards.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223969%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22women%20working%20out%20at%20lumin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3e9257a3d27148878c307%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224172%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClasses%20at%20Lumin%20Fitness%20are%20gamified%20to%20instill%20motivation.%20%3Cp%3ELumin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAttendees%20can%20accumulate%20digital%20currencies%20known%20as%20Lumin%20coins%20in%20exchange%20for%20trial%20memberships%2C%20solo%20classes%20for%20friends%2C%20and%20clothes%20and%20gift%20cards%20from%20the%20gym's%20online%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20classes%20are%20led%20by%20personal%20AI%20trainers%2C%20they%20are%20supervised%20by%20a%20real%20fitness%20professional%20in%20case%20anything%20goes%20wrong.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lumin%20fitness%20coach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c644716fcb546d2d4df206%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221116%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20human%20fitness%20coach%20attends%20each%20class%20to%20ensure%20it%20goes%20smoothly.%3Cp%3ELumin%20Fitness%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20human%20coach's%20job%20is%20to%20assist%20the%20AI%20by%20creating%20a%20more%20personalized%20workout%20experience%20for%20each%20member.%20The%20coach%20is%20also%20there%20to%20build%20community%20in%20the%20room%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20costs%20range%20from%20%2489%20to%20%24209%20a%20month.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221318%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20people%20working%20out%20at%20lumin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3e97043bb77284ba4a92d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22876%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20people%20working%20out.%3Cp%3ELumin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cheapest%20package%2C%20which%20starts%20at%20%2489%20a%20month%2C%20includes%20four%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20expensive%20package%20starts%20at%20%24209%20a%20month%20and%20includes%20an%20unlimited%20number%20of%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOver%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20Lumin%20plans%20to%20open%20an%20additional%2013%20studios%20in%20other%20cities%20across%20Texas%2C%20including%20Austin%2C%20Houston%20and%20Dallas.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20standing%20in%20lumin%20fitness%20studio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3e9986fcb546d2d4d3a78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22972%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20woman%20standing%20in%20a%20fitness%20studio.%3Cp%3ELumin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELumin%20Fitness%20signed%20a%20deal%20with%20franchise%20partner%20Verge%20Fit%20Holdings%20for%20an%20additional%2013%20units%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it's%20currently%20in%20talks%20to%20license%20its%20AI%20technology%20to%20gym%20operators%20in%20both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20establishing%20training%20systems%20for%20athletes%20at%20two%20Division%201%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-powered-fitness-studio-gym-led-by-virtual-trainers-texas-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707648121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c6a2776fcb546d2d4e3a97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-powered-fitness-studio-gym-led-by-virtual-trainers-texas-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lumin%20Fitness'%20gym%20uses%20AI%20to%20track%20people's%20movements%20and%20offers%20classes%20led%20by%20a%20virtual%20trainer%2C%20which%20gives%20real-time%20feedback%20to%20fitness%20fans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22amok%40insider.com%20(Aaron%20Mok)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-powered-fitness-studio-gym-led-by-virtual-trainers-texas-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maxwell%20slams%20fifth%20T20I%20ton%20to%20equal%20Rohit%E2%80%99s%20record%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107600956%2Cimgsize-45760.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fglenn-maxwell-slams-fifth-t20i-hundred-to-equal-rohit-sharmas-record%2Farticleshow%2F107600996.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Glenn%20Maxwell%20slammed%20a%2050-ball%20century%20as%20Australia%20raced%20to%20241-4%20in%20the%20second%20of%20three%20Twenty20%20internationals%20against%20the%20West%20Indies%20in%20Adelaide%20on%20Sunday.%20The%2035-year-old%20was%20in%20ominous%20touch%2C%20coming%20to%20the%20crease%20with%20the%20hosts%20on%2064-3%20in%20the%20seventh%20over%20and%20blasting%20eight%20sixes%20and%2012%20fours%20in%20a%20blistering%20knock%20of%20120%20not%20out%20from%2055%20balls.%20The%20hosts%20won%20the%20first%20match%20in%20Hobart%20by%2011%20runs%20on%20the%20back%20of%2070%20from%20David%20Warner%20and%20the%20veteran%20was%20again%20ultra-aggressive%20at%20the%20start%20after%20they%20were%20sent%20in%20to%20bat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%2063-year-old%20explains%20how%20Blue%20Zones%20helped%20him%20rethink%20his%20retirement%20plan%20to%20avoid%20his%20'biggest%20fear'%20of%20loneliness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223915%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rear%20view%20of%20man%20standing%20on%20a%20dock%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3c32a6fcb546d2d4d1449%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222353%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEd%2C%2063%2C%20not%20pictured%2C%20is%20taking%20steps%20to%20ensure%20he%20isn't%20lonely%20when%20he%20enters%20retirement.%3Cp%3Ekeithsutherland%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEd%2C%2063%2C%20hasn't%20retired%20yet%2C%20but%20he%20wants%20to%20ensure%20he%20won't%20be%20lonely%20when%20he%20does.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDescribing%20loneliness%20as%20his%C2%A0%26quot%3Bbiggest%20fear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20plans%20to%20volunteer%20and%20pursue%20hobbies%20upon%20retirement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he's%20worried%20that%20older%20adults%20are%20getting%20cast%20to%20the%20side%20as%20they%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEd%2C%2063%2C%20was%20recently%20rewatching%20a%20documentary%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-zone-residents-longevity-secrets-traits-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlue%20Zones%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20led%20him%20to%20rethink%20his%20outlook%20on%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Zones%20are%20regions%20in%20the%20world%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-5-blue-zones-people-live-longest-lives-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhere%20people%20are%20believed%20to%20live%20the%20longest%2C%20healthiest%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20people%20who%20live%20in%20those%20zones%20have%20traits%20that%20include%20living%20with%20purpose%20and%20maintaining%20relationships%20with%20friends%20starting%20at%20a%20young%20age.%20Ed%20%E2%80%94%20who%20requested%20his%20last%20name%20be%20withheld%20for%20privacy%20but%20whose%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20Business%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%20said%20there's%20no%20reason%20he%20can't%20incorporate%20those%20ideals%20into%20his%20own%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20people%20were%20actively%20engaged%20in%20their%20community%2C%20they%20were%20doing%20things%2C%20they%20were%20gardening%2C%20they%20were%20actively%20involved%2C%20they%20had%20good%20mobility.%20They%20didn't%20suffer%20any%20of%20the%20degenerative%20ills%20that%20we%20as%20North%20Americans%20suffer%2C%26quot%3B%20Ed%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Blue%20Zone%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20that's%20part%20and%20parcel%20where%20some%20of%20my%20insight%20comes%20from%2C%20that%20I%20think%20to%20retire%20and%20to%20suddenly%20stop%20and%20to%20say%2C%20'Well%20now%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%20nothing%2C'%20is%20going%20to%20kill%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Ed%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20absolutely%20convinced%20of%20that.%20I%20think%20being%20sedentary%20and%20not%20engaged%20is%20the%20worst%20thing%20that%20you%20can%20put%20upon%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20moving%20from%20Connecticut%20to%20Ontario%2C%20Canada%2C%20in%20the%2080s%2C%20Ed%20has%20worked%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20industry%2C%20and%20he's%20not%20sure%20when%20he'll%20officially%20retire.%20But%20he's%20making%20plans%20for%20when%20that%20day%20comes%20to%20avoid%20what%20he%20said%20is%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fabout%2Fnews%2F2023%2F05%2F03%2Fnew-surgeon-general-advisory-raises-alarm-about-devastating-impact-epidemic-loneliness-isolation-united-states.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bbiggest%20fear%26quot%3B%3A%20being%20lonely%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20hopes%20that%20upon%20retirement%2C%20he%20can%20pursue%20his%20passion%20for%20bas-relief%20art%2C%20which%20is%20a%20type%20of%20sculpting%20to%20create%20three-dimensional%20figures%20mounted%20on%20two-dimensional%20surfaces%2C%20like%20the%20figures%20on%20certain%20coins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20plans%20to%20volunteer%20at%20nonprofit%20organizations%20and%20shelters%20to%20ensure%20that%20retiring%20from%20his%20job%20doesn't%20also%20mean%20retiring%20from%20social%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20for%20some%20older%20adults%2C%20it's%20not%20always%20that%20easy.%20US%20Surgeon%20General%20Vivek%20Murthy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fabout%2Fnews%2F2023%2F05%2F03%2Fnew-surgeon-general-advisory-raises-alarm-about-devastating-impact-epidemic-loneliness-isolation-united-states.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclared%20loneliness%20an%20epidemic%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alongside%20data%20showing%20poor%20social%20interaction%20could%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%2C%20stroke%2C%20and%20dementia%20among%20older%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEd%20said%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20brighter%20spotlight%20on%20this%20crisis%20because%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20alone%20has%20got%20to%20be%20the%20worst%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20that%20are%20suffering%20from%20loneliness%20simply%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20contacts%2C%20their%20children%20aren't%20paying%20attention%20to%20them%2C%20or%20they're%20estranged%20from%20them%20for%20whatever%20reason%20or%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BSo%20being%20alone%20is%20something%20that%20does%20concern%20me.%20And%20I've%20always%20said%20to%20my%20wife%2C%20'Geez%2C%20I%20hope%20I%20go%20before%20you%20do%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20left.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'I%20needed%20to%20do%20something'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEd%20said%20he%20found%20himself%20thinking%20negatively%20about%20his%20retirement%20outlook%20and%20the%20way%20his%20job%20defines%20who%20he%20is%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20knew%20that%20if%20he%20wanted%20to%20avoid%20loneliness%2C%20his%20thought%20process%20needed%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20to%20think%20of%20myself%20in%20terms%20of%20not%20being%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20Ed%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20working%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%20you're%20contributing%2C%20you're%20providing%2C%20and%20suddenly%20that%20stops%2C%20the%20thing%20that%20looms%20in%20the%20distance%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20relevancy%20because%20we%20all%20tend%20to%20identify%20with%20what%20we%20do%20for%20a%20living.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20thinking%20in%20terms%20of%20whether%20or%20not%20I'm%20still%20even%20valid%2C%20and%20I%20came%20to%20realize%20these%20are%20not%20good%20thoughts%20and%20I%20needed%20to%20do%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ed%20is%20proactively%20planning%20for%20when%20he%20no%20longer%20has%20his%20job%2C%20BI%20has%20previously%20spoken%20to%20some%20older%20adults%20who%20were%20experiencing%20loneliness%20post-retirement%20and%20took%20matters%20into%20their%20own%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Lamy%2C%20a%2075-year-old%20retiree%20in%20Seattle%2C%20decided%20to%20address%20his%20loneliness%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-crisis-retiree-how-to-achieve-happiness-budget-retirement-seniors-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarting%20a%20group%20at%20his%20senior%20center%20where%20people%20can%20simply%20gather%20and%20chat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20lifesaver%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20similar%20to%20Ed's%20concerns%2C%20leaving%20his%20job%20cut%20%26quot%3Boff%20a%20huge%20flow%20of%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Rick%20Grossman%2C%20a%2070-year-old%20who%20battled%20loneliness%20throughout%20his%20life%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenior-villages-loneliness-making-friends-in-retirement-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20a%20solution%20through%20a%20%26quot%3Bsenior%20village%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20community%20that%20connects%20older%20adults%20in%20the%20same%20region%20to%20resources%20and%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20when%20I%20would've%20just%20stayed%20home%20alone%2C%20and%20now%20I%20will%20do%20some%20of%20the%20things%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20before%2C%20like%20go%20to%20the%20movies%20or%20to%20dinner%2C%26quot%3B%20Grossman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'The%20necessity%20of%20being%20engaged'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20significant%20mental%20and%20physical%20impacts%20of%20experiencing%20loneliness%2C%20Ed%20said%20he%20believes%20the%20%26quot%3Bsystemic%20issues%26quot%3B%20of%20lacking%20social%20interaction%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20nationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20not%20careful%20at%20this%20stage%20of%20my%20life%2C%20my%20life%20expectancy%20will%20diminish%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20overall%20well-being%20is%20definitely%20tied%20to%20my%20family%20and%20my%20relationships%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20the%20currency%20is.%20It's%20about%20the%20simple%20act%20and%20the%20necessity%20of%20being%20engaged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Murthy's%20efforts%20to%20bring%20awareness%20to%20the%20loneliness%20epidemic%2C%20some%20lawmakers%20are%20hoping%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20in%20Congress.%20Democratic%20Sens.%20Chris%20Murphy%20and%20Bob%20Casey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.murphy.senate.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fmurphy-casey-introduce-bill-to-fight-social-isolation-and-loneliness-among-older-americans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduced%20a%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%20%E2%80%94%20called%20Addressing%20Social%20Isolation%20and%20Loneliness%20in%20Older%20Adults%20Act%20%E2%80%94%20to%20establish%20grants%20and%20training%20for%20community-based%20organizations%20to%20help%20address%20loneliness%20in%20older%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20federal%20efforts%20progress%2C%20Ed%20wants%20to%20ensure%20loneliness%20among%20older%20people%20is%20a%20concern%20that%20all%20age%20groups%20work%20to%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20an%20indebtedness%20to%20the%20people%20that%20raised%20us%2C%20the%20generation%20that%20came%20before%2C%20and%20we%20cannot%20discard%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Ed%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20that%20what%20we're%20looking%20at%20here%20in%20North%20America%2C%20Canada%20as%20well%2C%20too%2C%20is%20a%20systemic%20occurrence%20where%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20make%20the%20time.%20And%20that's%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-solve-loneliness-older-adult-planning-retirement-biggest-fear-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c3c3327a3d271488789c04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-solve-loneliness-older-adult-planning-retirement-biggest-fear-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20loneliness%20continues%20to%20hit%20older%20Americans%20particularly%20hard%2C%20Ed%2C%2063%2C%20is%20doing%20everything%20he%20can%20to%20avoid%20that%20outcome%20once%20he%20retires.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%