ld%20get%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20ran%20through%20her%20work%20experience%20and%20had%20pre-recorded%20references%20from%20former%20colleagues%20and%20friends%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20process%20took%20about%2010%20hours%2C%20she%20said.%20After%20it%20was%20done%2C%20Kobayashi%20used%20ContactOut%2C%20an%20email%20lookup%20tool%2C%20to%20send%20it%20directly%20to%20the%20hiring%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fmarianadkobayashi_if-youre-going-to-apply-for-a-dream-company-ugcPost-7090602040061489152-gj0r%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20the%20video%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20quickly%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3AugcPost%3A7090602040061489152%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLots%20of%20people%20reached%20out%20to%20me%20offering%20coffee%20chats%20and%20letting%20me%20know%20about%20positions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%20the%20recruiter%20for%20the%20role%20reached%20out%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20call%20with%20her.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20'purpose-driven'%20application%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKobayashi%20said%20the%20Google%20recruiter%20told%20her%20she%20was%20overqualified%20for%20the%20grad%20scheme%20she'd%20applied%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20said%20she%20was%20impressed%20with%20the%20video%20and%20Kobayashi's%20LinkedIn%20content%20and%20promised%20to%20keep%20her%20in%20the%20pipeline%20for%20further%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20followed%20up%20every%20two%20months%2C%20letting%20her%20know%20my%20progress%20and%20what%20I%20was%20up%20to.%20In%20September%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20position%20for%20an%20account%20executive%2C%26quot%3B%20Kobayashi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKobayashi%20said%20she%20was%20able%20to%20get%20a%20referral%20from%20a%20friend%20and%20applied%20immediately%20despite%20being%20slightly%20underqualified%20for%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recruiter%20also%20reached%20out%20about%20the%20role%2C%20offering%20to%20connect%20her%20with%20the%20hiring%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20very%20purpose-driven%20application%2C%20so%20I%20think%20that%20made%20me%20stand%20out%2C%20and%20then%20because%20the%20recruiter%20was%20already%20kind%20of%20on%20my%20side%2C%20that%20helped%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAcknowledging%20her%20'red%20flags'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKobayashi%20said%20she%20sent%20out%20two%20documents%20after%20the%20interviews.%20One%20highlighted%20why%20a%20company%20should%20hire%20her%20and%20another%20detailed%20what%20she%20perceived%20as%20her%20%26quot%3Bred%20flags%26quot%3B%20or%20employment%20gaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20document%20saying%3A%20'This%20is%20why%20you%20should%20not%20hire%20me%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20also%20included%20a%20page%20saying%3A%20'This%20is%20how%20I'm%20going%20to%20turn%20my%20red%20flags%20into%20green%20flags.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20lacked%20sales%20experience%20and%20wanted%20to%20acknowledge%20this%20while%20showing%20she%20had%20a%20plan%20to%20address%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20three-step%20interview%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20interview%20involved%20three%20stages%20of%20roughly%2045-minute%20calls%2C%20including%20a%20case%20study%20and%20a%20leadership%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20an%20interview%2C%20I'd%20send%20them%20the%20documents%2C%20and%20they%20loved%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20the%20interview%20process%2C%20she%20followed%20up%20with%20the%20recruiter%20weekly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20wait%20one%20month%20until%20I%20got%20a%20response%20telling%20me%20I%20was%20in%20the%20final%20pool%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20week%20later%2C%20I%20got%20a%20job%20offer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-landed-role-google-viral-video-laid-off-how-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c6648b6fcb546d2d4e1519%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-landed-role-google-viral-video-laid-off-how-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mariana%20Kobayashi%20also%20sent%20recruiters%20documents%20that%20highlighted%20her%20%26quot%3Bred%20flags%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20her%20strengths%2C%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-landed-role-google-viral-video-laid-off-how-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Talking%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07131439%2FIMG_0107-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COn%20principle%20it%20is%20quite%20wrong%20to%20try%20founding%20a%20theory%20on%20observable%20magnitude%20alone.%20In%20reality%20the%20very%20opposite%20happens.%20It%20is%20the%20theory%20which%20decides%20what%20we%20can%20observe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%88%BC%20Albert%20Einstein%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%205%2C%202024%2C%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttarakhand%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20tabled%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20Bill%20.%20The%20rather%20complex%20document%20(with%20seven%20schedules%20and%20392%20sections)%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20House%20the%20very%20next%20day.%20Uttarakhand%20thus%20becomes%20the%20first%20state%20in%20independent%20India%20to%20pass%20a%20common%20law%20on%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%20and%20even%20live-in%20relationships%20between%20two%20consenting%20adults.%20The%20hurry%20with%20which%20the%20Bill%20was%20brought%20and%20passed%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%202024%20elections%20clearly%20indicates%20a%20similar%20passage%20for%20the%20Bill%20in%20all%20other%20states%2C%20should%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20win%20with%20a%20large%20majority%2C%20of%20which%20they%20seem%20very%20sure.%20And%20when%20that%20is%20done%20we%20will%20have%20a%20pan-Indian%20civil%20society%20the%20BJP%20wishes%20to%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20293px)%2085vw%2C%20293px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22293%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22357%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20swiftly%20released%20press%20note%20from%20a%20group%20of%20Uttarakhandi%20women%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20Bill%20became%20public%2C%20the%20women%20of%20Uttarakhand%20had%20protested%20and%20rejected%20the%20draft%20in%20toto.%20According%20to%20the%20note%20which%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20disregarded%2C%20the%20Bill%20was%20built%20along%20the%20patriarchal%20Hindu%20law%20template%20and%20retained%20several%20discriminatory%20aspects%20that%20would%20deny%20women%20an%20equal%20agency%20.%20The%20leaders%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20have%20also%20protested%20over%20the%20UCC%20overtaking%20Muslim%20personal%20laws.%20The%20new%20law%20lacks%20clarity%20for%20both%20groups%20and%20that%20may%20cause%20heavy%20snarls%20when%20it%20is%20implemented.%20It%20does%20not%2C%20for%20example%2C%20distinguish%20between%20ancestral%20or%20self-acquired%20property.%20It%20seems%20to%20promote%20intrusive%20moral%20policing%20and%20may%20result%20in%C2%A0%20discriminatory%20harassment%20of%20adults%20in%20a%20relationship%20that%20has%20been%20considered%20autonomous%20and%20consensual.%20Some%20of%20the%20rules%20may%20become%20clearer%20when%20gazetted%20but%20the%20compulsory%20registration%20of%20live-in%20relationships%20is%20full%20of%20explosive%20landmines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202005%2C%20when%20the%20Hindu%20Succession%20(Amendment)%20Act%20was%20passed%20thus%20giving%20daughters%20equal%20coparcenary%20rights%20in%20ancestral%20property%2C%20the%20then%20law%20minister%20was%20asked%20by%20the%20distinguished%20lawyer%20Fali%20Nariman%20whether%20his%20government%20would%20follow%20this%20with%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20binding%20on%20all%20Indians.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20speak%20for%20all%20communities%20unless%20they%20are%20ready.%E2%80%9D%20This%20care%20for%20the%20sentiments%20and%20reservations%20among%20the%20actual%20stakeholders%20was%20mostly%20lacking%20in%20the%20preparation%20and%20the%20hasty%20passage%20of%20the%20UCC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20grassroots%20reality%2C%20was%20even%20the%20Hindu%20community%20of%20Uttarakhand%20prepped%20and%20well%20informed%20about%20the%20various%20provisions%20of%20the%20new%20law%3F%20Does%20it%20know%20that%20the%201.89%25%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20population%20has%20been%20kept%20out%20of%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Bill%2C%20and%20has%20(according%20to%20a%20report%20based%20on%20the%20NFHS%20survey%202021)%20a%20higher%20percentage%20of%20men%20marrying%20more%20than%20one%20wife%20than%20the%20Muslims%20in%20the%20state%3F%20So%20far%20as%20one%20knows%2C%20there%20was%20no%20well%20publicised%20and%20wide%20dialogue%20between%20citizens%E2%80%99%20groups%20(especially%20the%20women%20whom%20it%20impacts%20the%20most)%20and%20the%20creators%20of%20the%20draft.%20Due%20care%20was%20also%20not%20taken%20to%20depoliticise%20the%20Bill%20by%20placing%20it%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20not%20before%20but%20after%20the%20general%20elections.%20Can%20we%20then%20pooh-pooh%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups%20and%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20political%20move%20to%20consolidate%20majority%20votes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Not%20in%20the%20Name%20of%20Gender%20Justice%3A%20Reflections%20on%20Uttarakhand's%20UCC%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnot-in-the-name-of-gender-justice-reflections-on-the-uttarakhands-ucc%5C%22%3ENot%20in%20the%20Name%20of%20Gender%20Justice%3A%20Reflections%20on%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20UCC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20obvious%2C%20as%20the%20press%20note%20from%20the%20dissenting%20group%20of%20women%20says%2C%20that%20the%20State%20can%20now%20reach%20deep%20inside%20personal%20spaces%2C%20even%20invade%20the%20privacy%20of%20citizens%E2%80%99%20bedrooms.%20Supporters%20deem%20the%20UCC%20a%20progressive%20step%20that%20would%20protect%20women%20in%20live-in%20relationships%20against%20domestic%20violence%20and%20confer%20legitimacy%20and%20property%20rights%20on%20any%20children%20born%20out%20of%20wedlock.%20But%20these%20provisions%20already%20existed%20under%20the%20federal%20laws%20such%20as%20the%20Domestic%20Violence%20Act.%20And%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20already%20ruled%20that%20live-in%20relationships%20are%20not%20criminal.%20Goa%20has%20had%20a%20pre-independence%20UCC%20that%20protects%20such%20unions.%20Did%20the%20draft%20makers%20even%20consult%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20more%20unsettling%20is%20that%20the%20government%20has%20not%20only%20not%20created%20widespread%20awareness%20about%20the%20hows%20and%20whys%20about%20new%20provisions%20of%20the%20UCC%2C%20it%20has%20also%20not%20produced%20necessary%20documentation%20to%20pass%20around%20among%20citizens.%20This%20means%20that%20many%20people%2C%20especially%20the%20young%20men%20and%20women%2C%20may%20find%20that%20they%20are%20law%20violators%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20State%20because%20they%20have%20not%20submitted%20necessary%20documentation%20to%20a%20registrar%20within%2030%20days%20of%20their%20union.%20This%20failure%20may%20subject%20them%20to%20heavy%20penalties%20and%20even%20long%20jail%20sentences%2C%20without%20being%20told%20in%20clear%20terms%20how%20and%20why.%20In%20a%20state%20with%20a%20small%20but%20diverse%20population%20following%20various%20faiths%20and%20personal%20laws%2C%20with%20a%20sizeable%20rural%20population%20living%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20any%20information%20needs%20time%20to%20reach%20and%20be%20absorbed%20by%20the%20locals.%20A%20sudden%20imposition%20of%20a%20UCC%20can%20trigger%20immediate%20and%20unforeseen%20social%2C%20political%2C%20legal%20and%20constitutional%20implications%20for%20Uttarakhandis.%20With%20the%20prolonged%20vituperative%20talk%20against%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%20and%20repeated%20underlining%20in%20media%20messages%20about%20how%20the%20law%20will%20free%20Muslim%20women%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eiddat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20bigamy%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20intent%20is%20more%20political%20than%20reformist%20and%20protective%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20intent%2C%20the%20UCC%20can%20not%20be%20faulted.%20It%20proposes%20to%20standardise%20the%20minimum%20age%20of%20marriage%20for%20all%20(already%20standardised%20for%20most%20citizens)%2C%20outlaw%20extra-judicial%20marital%20norms%20that%20exploited%20women%2C%20prohibit%20polygamy%20and%20promise%20equal%20inheritance%20to%20both%20men%20and%20women.%20Given%20how%20women%20have%20been%20exploited%20along%20these%20issues%2C%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20the%20UCC%20is%20in%20itself%20a%20good%20idea.%20But%20the%20present%20UCC%20law%20is%20full%20of%20holes.%20Take%20the%20mandatory%20registration%20(within%2060%20days)%20of%20the%20relationship%20and%20the%20punitive%20proceedings%20that%20will%20follow%20swiftly%20in%20case%20of%20failure%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20lack%20of%20public%20awareness%20about%20the%20new%20laws%20can%20easily%20hand%20the%20State%20a%20new%20tool%20and%20if%20it%20so%20desires%2C%20to%20cherry%20pick%20political%20dissenters%20and%20minorities%20to%20harass%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Centre%20opposed%20same-sex%20marriage%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20it%20did%20so%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20marriage%20is%20inherently%20connected%20to%20religious%20and%20cultural%20norms.%20Why%20has%20this%20autonomy%20for%20religio-cultural%20norms%20suddenly%20been%20discarded%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20registrar%20criminalising%20live-in%20relationships%20because%20the%20couple%20may%20have%20come%20to%20him%20not%20within%20the%20mandated%20period%3F%20Also%20it%20is%20unclear%20when%20couples%20go%20to%20him%20how%20he%20will%20verify%20the%20details%20provided%20by%20them.%20He%20may%20choose%20someone%20who%20can%20%E2%80%9Cconduct%20enquiry%20to%20establish%20validity%20of%20the%20relationship%E2%80%9D.%20The%20use%20of%20phrases%20to%20describe%20prohibited%20relationships%20under%20titles%20like%20%E2%80%98legitimate%20blood%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98half%20blood%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98uterine%20blood%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98full%20blood%E2%80%99%20in%20an%20actual%20legal%20document%20is%20mind%20boggling%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20Who%20can%20the%20registrar%20summon%20when%20judging%20a%20case%20of%20live-in%20relationship%3F%20An%20angry%20parent%20%3F%20A%20cousin%20with%20a%20score%20to%20settle%3F%20An%20RWA%20uncle%20who%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20registrar%20who%20maintains%20the%20register%20of%20all%20such%20couples%3F%20The%20local%20Thanadhyaksh%20ji%3F%20Is%20the%20registrar%20allowed%20to%20share%20this%20register%20of%20couples%20in%20live-in%20relationship%20with%20the%20local%20police%20station%3F%20Is%20it%20a%20public%20register%20anyone%20can%20access%20like%20other%20registers%20listed%20in%20the%20new%20law%20(Part%201%2C%20Chapter%202)%20pertaining%20to%20marriages%2C%20divorces%20etc.%3F%20If%20it%20is%2C%20what%20prevents%20the%20local%20moral%20policing%20groups%20from%20intruding%20into%20the%20bedrooms%20of%20%E2%80%98suspected%E2%80%99%20citizens%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20time%20to%20recall%20that%20the%20State%20has%20not%20created%20either%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage%20or%20live-in%20relationships.%20Society%20and%20the%20changing%20times%20have.%20Each%20law%20is%20a%20society%E2%80%99s%20text%2C%20a%20reflection%20of%20its%20rational%20mind.%20But%20our%20judiciary%2C%20legislature%2C%20executive%20and%20the%20media%20are%20all%20glaringly%20minority%20and%20female%20deficient.%20So%20even%20if%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20milk%20of%20human%20kindness%20flowing%20in%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20veins%2C%20the%20State%20must%20show%20proof%20of%20its%20sincerity%20in%20recognising%20the%20enormity%20and%20complexity%20of%20the%20task%20of%20giving%20us%20a%20just%20and%20fair%20%C2%A0UCC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07131439%2FIMG_0107-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftalking-uniform-civil-code%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20its%20intent%2C%20the%20UCC%20can%20not%20be%20faulted.%20But%20the%20present%20Uttarakhand%20UCC%20law%20is%20full%20of%20holes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftalking-uniform-civil-code%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sneak%20peek%20inside%20Rose's%20lavish%20lifestyle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107599591%2Cimgsize-113026.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fross-net-worth-luxurious-home-car-collection-sneak-peek-inside-the-blackpink-stars-lavish-lifestyle%2Fphotostory%2F107599591.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107599591.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERos%C3%A9's%20net%20worth%2C%20luxurious%20home%2C%20car%20collection%3A%20Sneak%20peek%20inside%20the%20BLACKPINK%20star's%20lavish%20lifestyle%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BTS's%20RM%20sends%20ARMY%20Lunar%20New%20Year%20note%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107600603%2Cimgsize-29830.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbtss-rm-sends-heartfelt-lunar-new-year-message-to-fans-from-military-service%2Farticleshow%2F107600653.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107600653.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBTS%20member%20RM%2C%20amidst%20military%20service%2C%20shares%20an%20update%20from%20the%20military.%20He%20expressed%20his%20commitment%20to%20learning%20and%20staying%20healthy%2C%20while%20also%20extending%20warm%20wishes%20for%20Lunar%20New%20Year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Boroline%20Saga%3A%20From%20a%20Symbol%20of%20the%20Swadeshi%20Movement%20to%20a%20Bengali%20Household%20Staple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11155422%2FBoroline_Antiseptic_Cream.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20when%20India%20gained%20independence%20from%20British%20rule%2C%20two%20of%20Calcutta%E2%80%99s%20newspapers%20announced%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fboroline.com%2Fabout-boroline%2F%5C%22%3Eone%20lakh%20Boroline%20tubes%20would%20be%20distributed%20for%20free%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoroline%20was%20first%20launched%20in%201929%20by%20a%20Bengali%20merchant%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173787%2Fbengal-boroline-gd-pharmaceutical-swadeshi-movement-india%2F%5C%22%3EGour%20Mohun%20Dutta.%3C%2Fa%3E%20It%20was%20then%20colloquially%20called%20%3Cem%3Ehaatiwala%3C%2Fem%3E%20cream%20(the%20cream%20with%20the%20elephant)%20because%20of%20its%20iconic%20white%20elephant%20logo%20on%20the%20green%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20product%20has%20managed%20to%20weather%20the%20eddy%20and%20flow%20of%20market%20change%20and%20is%20still%20just%20as%20relevant%20today%20as%20it%20was%2095%20years%20ago.%20Against%20all%20odds%2C%20Boroline%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20colonial%20Indian%20market%20as%20an%20effective%20and%20potent%20alternative%20to%20imported%20foreign%20creams.%20Coupled%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhomegrown.co.in%2Fhomegrown-voices%2Fswadeshi-identity-bengali-nostalgia-the-history-of-indias-first-antiseptic-cream%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Swadeshi%E2%80%99%20sentiments%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20effort%20to%20promote%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20self-sufficiency%2C%20Boroline%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20soon%20swept%20over%20the%20entire%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20amidst%20the%20fervour%20of%20Swadeshi%20sentiments%2C%20Indians%20readily%20boycotted%20all%20foreign%20goods%20and%20embraced%20this%20multipurpose%20antiseptic%20cream%20that%20entered%20the%20market%20at%20that%20opportune%20moment%20at%20a%20cheap%20price.%20During%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20G.D.%20Pharmaceutical%20sold%20the%20cream%20in%20any%20container%20available%2C%20with%20a%20label%20at%20the%20bottom%20that%20promised%2C%20%E2%80%9COriginal%20packing%20changed%20due%20to%20war%20emergency%2C%20quantity%20and%20quality%20of%20contents%20remain%20unaltered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20small%20cut%20wounds%2C%20scabs%2C%20chapped%20and%20dried%20skin%20to%20extra%20moisturisation%20during%20chilly%20weather%20%E2%80%93%20a%20thick%20layer%20of%20Boroline%20cream%20soon%20became%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20for%20all%20skin-related%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHenceforth%2C%20the%20product%20became%20synonymous%20with%20Indian%20cultural%20identity%2C%20serving%20folks%20living%20in%20the%20cold%20Himalayan%20regions%20and%20the%20Southern%20plains%20of%20the%20country%2C%20with%20the%20same%20measure%20of%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20curious%20thing%20about%20this%20product%20is%20its%20enduring%20popularity%20against%20the%20plethora%20of%20multinational%20brands%20that%20have%20been%20flooding%20the%20market%20with%20innovative%20formulations%20every%20few%20months.%20The%20antiseptic%20formula%20of%20Boroline%20%E2%80%93%20boric%20acid%20mixed%20with%20zinc%20oxide%20%3Cem%3E(jasad%20bhasma%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20paraffin%20and%20oleum%2C%20infused%20with%20a%20unique%20fragrance%20%E2%80%93%20is%20hardly%20a%20secret.%20Yet%20a%20deluge%20of%20innovative%20skincare%20products%20and%20counterfeit%20products%20entering%20the%20market%20every%20year%20fails%20to%20dupe%20Boroline%20users%2C%20without%20any%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20a%20brand%20with%20Boroline%E2%80%99s%20equity%2C%20it%20generates%20a%20yearly%20revenue%20of%20only%20Rs%20150%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20underwhelming%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FHome-Page%2FlPdtZPKn9F1l2OZogkJSoJ%2FIts-business-as-usual-for-87yearold-Boroline.html%5C%22%3ERoopen%20Roy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20managing%20director%20of%20Deloitte%20Consulting%20India%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebashish%20Dutta%2C%20grandson%20of%20Gour%20Mohun%20Dutta%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FCompanies%2FBvkIFoi2YFIY7RtiarEaRN%2FOur-thrust-will-be-on-expanding-Boroline-Suthols-retail-pe.html%5C%22%3ELivemint%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%20sure%20that%20our%20successful%20products%20are%20consistent%E2%80%94they%20don%E2%80%99t%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20have%20found%20that%20such%20a%20conservative%20attitude%20towards%20change%20is%20a%20common%20trait%20in%20most%20Bengali%20business%20ventures.%20They%20tend%20to%20target%20a%20very%20specific%20and%20old%20customer%20base%2C%20focusing%20more%20on%20quality%20than%20the%20numbers%20on%20the%20profit%20scale%20and%20refusing%20to%20compete%20with%20short-term%20market%20trends.%20Their%20reservation%20towards%20scaling%20up%20is%20quite%20possibly%20a%20precautionary%20response%20to%20the%20immense%20loss%20once%20incurred%20by%20the%20Bengali%20merchants%20during%20their%20trade%20with%20the%20British%20in%20the%20colonial%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20G.D.%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%202003%20launch%2C%20the%20antiseptic%20liquid%20Suthol%2C%20has%20diversified%20its%20market%20and%20is%20rapidly%20growing%20in%20popularity.%20It%20accounts%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FHome-Page%2FlPdtZPKn9F1l2OZogkJSoJ%2FIts-business-as-usual-for-87yearold-Boroline.html%5C%22%3E30%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20GD%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%20sales%20currently%2C%20showing%20remarkable%20growth%20on%20a%20year-on-year%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EG.D.%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20consistency%20has%20been%20equivocally%20rewarded%20by%20its%20customer%20base%2C%20even%20by%20the%20globe-trotting%20Bengali%20communities%20of%20the%20present%20day.%20Multiple%20tubs%20of%20Boroline%20go%20through%20customs%20at%20various%20airports%20every%20year%20when%20Bengalis%20move%20abroad%20for%20study%20or%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuchetana%20Chatterjee%2C%20a%20student%20living%20in%20Munich%2C%20swears%20by%20Boroline%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20tried%20tons%20of%20skincare%20products%2C%20and%20in%20-10%20degrees%2C%20nothing%20works%20as%20good%20as%20Boroline%2C%20also%20vouched%20for%20by%20some%20of%20my%20international%20friends!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShorbori%20Biswas%2C%20currently%20living%20in%20Georgia%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20use%20Boroline%20in%20Tbilisi%20as%20well%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20best%20for%20dry%20skin%20like%20mine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjini%20Mahalanobish%2C%20who%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Philadelphia%20for%20a%20few%20years%20now%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20stock%20up%20on%20%5BBoroline%5D%20on%20each%20visit%20to%20India.%20Its%20proven%20effectiveness%20and%20affordability%20make%20it%20my%20go-to%20choice%2C%20echoing%20a%20habit%20passed%20on%20by%20my%20grandparents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnwesha%20Das%2C%20a%20student%20at%20TU%20Delft%2C%20Netherlands%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20brought%20along%20five%20tubs%20to%20last%20me%20as%20long%20as%20I%20was%20away%20from%20home.%20Mum%20and%20I%20applying%20Boroline%20on%20our%20elbows%20and%20lips%20had%20been%20our%20nighttime%20ritual%20long%20before%20these%20popular%20skincare%20potions%20hit%20the%20market%20and%20this%20is%20a%20habit%20I%E2%80%99d%20never%20grow%20out%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengali%20community%E2%80%99s%20close%20relationship%20with%20the%20moss-green%20tube%20of%20Boroline%20is%20laced%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20nostalgia%2C%20community%20pride%2C%20and%20faith%20in%20a%20product%20that%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDebabratee%20Dhar%20was%20an%20intern%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11155422%2FBoroline_Antiseptic_Cream.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fthe-boroline-saga-from-a-symbol-of-the-swadeshi-movement-to-a-bengali-household-staple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22G.D.%20Pharma%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20consistency%20has%20been%20equivocally%20rewarded%20by%20its%20customer%20base%2C%20even%20by%20the%20globe-trotting%20Bengali%20communities%20of%20the%20present%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fthe-boroline-saga-from-a-symbol-of-the-swadeshi-movement-to-a-bengali-household-staple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Violent%20protests%20erupt%20in%20Senegal%20against%20delayed%20presidential%20elections%3B%203%20dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707647126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107600779%2Cimgsize-1398658.cms%22%2C%2