ce%2C%20rather%20than%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20government%20roles%20may%20not%20require%20degrees%2C%20most%20jobs%20require%20certifications.%20The%20most%20common%20include%20CompTIA%2C%20ISC(2)%2C%20and%20ISACA.%20Some%20roles%20also%20require%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhandbook.tts.gsa.gov%2Fgeneral-information-and-resources%2Fbusiness-and-ops-policies%2Ftop-secret%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBelow%2520are%2520approximate%2520timelines%2520for%2CCompartmented%2520Information%2520(TS%252FSCI)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclearances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20take%20up%20to%20several%20months%20to%20get%20approved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20demand%20for%20tech%20continues%2C%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F01%2F29%2Ffact-sheet-biden-harris-administration-announces-key-ai-actions-following-president-bidens-landmark-executive-order%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTo%2520seize%2520AI%2527s%2520enormous%2520promise%2Ctrain%2520workers%2520with%2520AI%2520expertise.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunches%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20large-scale%20hiring%20initiative%20for%20AI%20specialists%2C%20many%20are%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20break%20into%20the%20business%20without%20paying%20for%20additional%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBenefits%20that%20are%20hard%20to%20pass%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGovernment%20jobs%20are%20famous%20for%20cushy%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Employee%20Retirement%20System%20(FERS)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20talked%20about%20benefits%20for%20employees%20working%20in%20the%20government%2C%20although%20government%20contractors%20don't%20offer%20this.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opm.gov%2Fretirement-center%2Ffers-information%2Ftypes-of-retirement%2F%23url%3DOverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGovernment%3C%2Fa%3E%20pensions%20offer%20retirees%20an%20annual%20income%20after%20they've%20stopped%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20amount%20depends%20on%20how%20many%20years%20an%20employee%20has%20worked%20and%20the%20age%20they're%20retiring%2C%20full%20benefits%20include%2070%25%20of%20an%20annual%20paycheck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20employees%20are%20ever%20in%20crisis%2C%20the%20government%20also%20offers%20EAP%2C%20which%20is%20an%20assistance%20program%20that%20offers%20employees%20legal%20advice%2C%20financial%20advice%2C%20and%20other%20resources%20that%20vary%20on%20the%20state%20or%20federal%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGovernment%20jobs%20also%20allow%20employees%20to%20travel%20domestically%20and%20abroad.%20Symon%C3%A9%20Berry%2C%20a%20government%20tech%20contractor%2C%20worked%20abroad%20for%20about%20five%20years%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20contract%20work%20abroad%2C%20she%20said%20all%20of%20her%20work-related%20expenses%20were%20paid%2C%20her%20salary%20was%20oftentimes%20untaxed%20due%20to%20agreements%20with%20other%20countries%2C%20and%20she%20received%20travel%20stipends%20dedicated%20to%20%26quot%3Brest%20and%20relaxation%26quot%3B%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20most%20government%20jobs%20provide%20tuition%20assistance%20to%20employees%20at%20a%20standard%20rate%20of%20%24250%20per%20credit%2C%20but%20some%20jobs%20will%20pay%20for%20the%20entire%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexxus%20Harris%2C%20an%20IT%20specialist%20for%20the%20CDC%2C%20said%20that%20her%20education%20was%20free%20because%20her%20schools%20matched%20the%20amount%20the%20government%20provided%20her.%20Harris%20obtained%20two%20degrees%20through%20the%20program%20and%20is%20interested%20in%20getting%20her%20Ph.D.%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20tuition%20assistance%2C%20the%20government%20also%20provides%20student%20loan%20forgiveness%20to%20government%20employees%20after%2010%20years%20of%20making%20payments.%20For%20Tamayo%2C%20this%20is%20the%20largest%20reason%20he%20stays%20in%20the%20public%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%