ses-linked-to-may-9-violence-case-5031350%5C%22%3Eas%20he%20serves%20time%20in%20jai%3C%2Fa%3El.%20Though%20Khan%20himself%20was%20barred%20from%20contesting%20due%20to%20a%20conviction%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%2C%20PTI%20candidates%2C%20who%20had%20to%20contest%20as%20independents%2C%20won%2091%20seats%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly.%20Though%20they%20are%20far%20from%20wresting%20power%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-election-results-2024-imran-khan-backed-independents-go-to-court-challenge-pakistan-poll-results-report-5034832%5C%22%3Ethe%20result%20%3C%2Fa%3Eindicates%20the%20success%20of%20a%20risky%20political%20strategy%20deployed%20by%20Khan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fpeople%2Fimran-khan-from-cricket-to-jail-with-layover-at-prime-ministers-office-5010784%5C%22%3Esince%20his%20ouster%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnTaking%20On%20The%20Military%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20played%20out%20in%20this%20election%20was%20eerily%20similar%20to%20what%20transpired%20in%202018.%20Only%2C%20the%20protagonists%20were%20differently%20placed.%20It%20was%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20who%20was%20sentenced%20to%20prison%20less%20than%20three%20weeks%20before%20the%20polls%20and%20Khan%20enjoyed%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-election-results-imran-khan-bilwal-bhutto-nawaz-sharif-no-clear-winner-in-pakistan-yet-imran-khan-party-protests-delay-in-results-5035050%5C%22%3Emilitary%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20allegations%20of%20the%20election%20not%20being%20free%20and%20fair%20were%20also%20similar%2C%20and%20the%20military%20was%20explicitly%20accused%20of%20interfering%20in%20the%20process%20to%20prop%20its%20blue-eyed%20boy%2C%20Khan%2C%20to%20the%20premiership.%20Khan%20ultimately%20became%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20but%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20all-powerful%20military%20soured%20within%20four%20years%20as%20he%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20meddling%20in%20the%20supposed%20civilian%20no-go%20zone%20of%20military%20and%20ISI%20(Inter-Services%20Intelligence)%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20out%20of%20power%2C%20Khan%20took%20on%20the%20military%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20manner.%20Within%20a%20month%20of%20being%20ousted%2C%20he%20led%20a%20%26quot%3Blong%20march%26quot%3B%20into%20Islamabad%20that%20turned%20violent.%20Another%20one%20in%20November%202022%20saw%20him%20being%20shot%20in%20the%20leg%20by%20a%20gunman%20who%20opened%20fire%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Wazirabad.%20Khan%20accused%20a%20senior%20army%20official%2C%20Major%20General%20Faisal%20Naseer%2C%20of%20the%20attempted%20assassination%20bid.%20In%20a%20rare%20statement%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20military%20rebutted%20the%20allegation%20by%20Khan.%20It%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20a%20consistent%20pattern%20for%20the%20last%20one%20year%20where%20military%20and%20intelligence%20agencies%20officials%20are%20targeted%20with%20insinuations%20and%20sensational%20propaganda%20for%20the%20furtherance%20of%20political%20objectives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan's%20constant%20tirades%20against%20the%20military%20saw%20an%20unusual%20and%20perhaps%20unimaginable%20outcome.%20The%20military%2C%20a%20formidable%20and%20unopposed%20power%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20saw%20violent%20attacks%20against%20itself%20in%20May%202023.%20Protesters%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20after%20Khan's%20arrest%20and%20were%20seen%20not%20just%20attacking%20the%20police%20and%20government%20buildings%20but%20also%20military%20installations.%20Shockingly%2C%20the%20army%20headquarters%20and%20an%20air%20force%20base%20were%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20early%20indications%20that%20Khan's%20political%20gamble%20of%20taking%20on%20the%20military%20had%20paid%20off.%20It%20was%20yielding%20dividends%2C%20and%20Khan's%20PTI%20was%20hopeful%20that%20it%20would%20bear%20even%20electoral%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhipping%20up%20anti-US%20sentiment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Pakistan%20economy%20tanked%20and%20Khan%20made%20an%20unceremonious%20exit%20from%20power%2C%20he%20trained%20his%20guns%20at%20the%20United%20States.%20Khan%20not%20only%20accused%20the%20US%20of%20being%20behind%20his%20ouster%20but%20also%20singled%20out%20US%20Assistant%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20South%20and%20Central%20Asian%20Affairs%2C%20Donald%20Lu%2C%20for%20conveying%20the%20same%20to%20the%20then-Pakistan%20ambassador%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Asad%20Majeed%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Khan%20himself%20said%20that%20Lu%20told%20Majeed%20Khan%20there%20would%20be%20implications%20if%20Khan%20was%20not%20removed.%20The%20meeting%2C%20as%20revealed%20later%2C%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Khan's%20visit%20to%20Moscow%20just%20as%20Russia%20attacked%20Ukraine%2C%20gravely%20upsetting%20Washington%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Khan%20continued%20to%20use%20the%20argument%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bforeign%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20behind%20his%20defeat%20in%20the%20no-confidence%20motion.%20The%20US%20denied%20the%20allegation%20of%20interference%20in%20Pakistani%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20victory%20of%20Khan's%20candidates%2C%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20released%20a%20statement%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20is%20prepared%20to%20work%20with%20the%20next%20Pakistani%20government%2C%20regardless%20of%20political%20party%2C%20to%20advance%20our%20shared%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20expressing%20concern%20over%20the%20allegations%20of%20election%20fraud%20-%20%26quot%3Bclaims%20of%20interference%20or%20fraud%20should%20be%20fully%20investigated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EPlaying%20Up%20The%20'Outsider'%20Threat%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20over%20the%20last