hrough%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20AICC%20general%20secretary%20in-charge%20of%20the%20state%20dismissed%20suggestions%20that%20the%20yatra%20was%20adversely%20affecting%20the%20poll%20preparations%20of%20the%20party%20and%20asserted%20that%20talks%20for%20seat-sharing%20with%20allies%20were%20going%20on%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20speak%2C%20we%20are%20finalising%20seat-sharing%20agreements%20with%20most%20of%20our%20allies%20in%20different%20states.%20So%20it%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20either%2For.%20The%20yatra%20is%20going%20on%20but%20other%20things%20are%20being%20handled%20by%20the%20AICC%20leadership%20and%20the%20state%20in-charges.%20The%20Congress%20president%20(Mallikarjun%20Kharge)%20is%20himself%20overseeing%20all%20these%20meetings%20and%20negotiations%20that%20are%20being%20held%2C%26quot%3B%20Pilot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20attempt%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20fight%20unitedly.%20Yes%20we%20have%20had%20some%20that%20have%20left%20our%20alliance%20but%20largely%20the%20alliance%20is%20intact%20and%20very%20soon%20we%20will%20be%20announcing%20the%20seat%20sharing%20and%20a%20future%20roadmap%20that%20the%20alliance%20will%20come%20up%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20suggestions%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20unravelling%20with%20JD(U)%20chief%20Nitish%20Kumar%20crossing%20over%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20RLD's%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20imminent%20switch-over%20and%20Ms%20Banerjee%20attacking%20the%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20amount%20of%20partners%20that%20left%20the%20NDA%20'%26quot%3B%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20PDP%2C%20AIADMK.%20So%20the%20number%20of%20those%20leaving%20the%20NDA%20is%20far%20larger%20than%20some%20of%20those%20people%20who%20may%20not%20be%20with%20us%20today.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20strong%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20we%20are%20having%20discussions%20with%20the%20TMC%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2046-year-old%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20switchover%20to%20the%20NDA%20raises%20the%20question%20of%20credibility%20also%20and%20he%20would%20have%20to%20answer%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%20when%20he%20goes%20to%20polls.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20may%20come%20and%20go%2C%20one%20or%20two%20moving%20sides%20will%20not%20make%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20effort%20we%20are%20putting%20in%20as%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%26quot%3B%20A%20one-on-one%20contest%20between%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20is%20tilted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20opposition%20coalition%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20with%20regards%20to%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20the%20final%20outcome%20will%20be%20a%20positive%20one.%20Every%20political%20party%20has%20its%20own%20turf%20to%20protect.%20A%20regional%20party%20will%20not%20want%20to%20cede%20too%20much%20space%2C%20as%20a%20national%20party%2C%20we%20also%20have%20an%20obligation%20to%20our%20state%20units.%20So%20there%20is%20always%20going%20to%20be%20some%20give%20and%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20the%20sensitivities%20of%20each%20of%20our%20partners%20but%20the%20final%20objective%20of%20the%20alliance%20is%20to%20come%20together%20and%20present%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20country%2C%20and%20we%20will%20achieve%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20%26quot%3Bstrong%26quot%3B%20and%20very%20soon%20it%20will%20announce%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20in%20different%20states%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20alliance%20will%20pose%20a%20%26quot%3Bformidable%20challenge%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20arithmetic%20calculation%20will%20show%20that%20the%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20over%2060%20per%20cent%20in%20the%202019%20elections%20and%20that%20of%20the%20NDA%20was%20around%2035%20per%20cent%2C%20therefore%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20does%20not%20come%20together%20whether%20it%20is%20by%20using%20central%20agencies%2C%20misinformation%2C%20propaganda%20or%20pressure%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLargely%20all%20this%20is%20futile%20because%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20strong.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%20and%20her%20primary%20objective%20is%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20will%20work%20together%20and%20find%20a%20way%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Pilot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20is%20a%20cause%20for%20worry%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20therefore%20%26quot%3Bthis%20frantic%20rejigging%20of%20the%20political%20landscape%20is%20happening%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20recent%20statement%20in%20Parliament%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20get%20370%20seats%20and%20the%20NDA%20over%20400%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%20Parliament%20is%20for%20discussing%20policy%20and%20legislation%20but%20that%20platform%20was%20used%20to%20make%20a%20purely%20political%20speech%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20sort%20of%20bravado%20and%20chest-thumping.%20I%20think%20the%20people%20of%20India%20will%20decide%20and%20no%20election%20is%20won%20or%20lost%20till%20the%20last%20vote%20is%20counted.%20I%20have%20great%20faith%20in%20the%20wisdom%20and%20objectivity%20of%20our%20voters%2C%20they%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20truth%20and%20propaganda%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20coming%20together%20is%20certainly%20a%20worry%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20this%20thing%20about%20%26quot%3B300%20paar%2C%20400%20paar%26quot%3B%20is%20more%20rhetoric%20than%20a%20true%20reflection%20of%20reality%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pilot%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP's%20poll%20plank%20is%20very%20unclear%20as%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20the%20people%20with%20its%2010-year%20report%20card%20or%20with%20a%20blueprint%20on%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20%26quot%3Brecord%20unemployment%2C%20skyrocketing%20inflation%2C%20agrarian%20distress%20and%20ever-increasing%20gap%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20poor%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20not%20come%20through%20on%20their%20commitments%20for%20doubling%20farmers'%20income%2C%20providing%20jobs%2C%20legal%20framework%20for%20MSP%2C%20or%20on%20eradicating%20black%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707639960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F4vid6gvo_sachin-pilot_625x300_11_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-sachin-pilot-india-rahul-gandhis-yatra-delaying-india-seats-decisions-sachin-pilots-reply-5036392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20some%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents%20switching%20sides%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20today%20said%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20is%20%26quot%3Bstrong%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20attempting%20a%20%26quot%3Bfrantic%20rejig%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20political%20landscape%20as%20it%20is%20worried%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-sachin-pilot-india-rahul-gandhis-yatra-delaying-india-seats-decisions-sachin-pilots-reply-5036392%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-sachin-pilot-india-rahul-gandhis-yatra-delaying-india-seats-decisions-sachin-pilots-reply-5036392%