22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fblackpinks-jisoo-birthday-message-for-ros%2Farticleshow%2F107598642.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107598642.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBLACKPINK's%20Jisoo%20celebrated%20Ros%C3%A9's%20birthday%20with%20a%20heartfelt%20message%2C%20emphasizing%20their%20genuine%20friendship.%20Jisoo's%20successful%20career%20includes%20projects%20like%20the%20drama%20'Influenza'%20and%20the%20movie%20'From%20the%20Reader's%20Point%20of%20View'.%20Lisa%20of%20BLACKPINK%20has%20recently%20launched%20her%20own%20artist%20management%20company%2C%20LLOUD.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Days%20Ahead%20Of%20Farmers'%20Protest%2C%20Haryana%20Issues%20An%20Order%20For%20Fuel%20Pumps%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%20connectivity%20has%20been%20suspended%20in%20seven%20districts%20as%20the%20BJP-led%20Haryana%20government%20gears%20up%20to%20block%20the%20farmers'%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20government%20has%20issued%20a%20notification%2C%20saying%20dongle%20services%20provided%20on%20mobile%20phones%2C%20will%20remain%20suspended%20and%20only%20voice%20calls%20would%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20are%20demanding%20a%20law%20to%20guarantee%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%20for%20their%20produce%20and%20pension%20and%20insurance%20schemes.%20More%20than%20200%20organisations%20are%20part%20of%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20internet%20services%20have%20been%20suspended%20in%20Ambala%2C%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Kaithal%2C%20Jind%2C%20Hisar%2C%20Fatehabad%20and%20Sirsa%20districts%20till%20Tuesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Haryana's%20Sonipat%2C%20located%20close%20to%20Delhi%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20has%20asked%20fuel%20pump%20owners%20to%20not%20fill%20up%20bottles%20or%20other%20containers.%20A%2010-litre%20cap%20has%20been%20introduced%20for%20tractors.%20The%20administration%20has%20warned%20that%20providing%20fuel%20to%20those%20associated%20with%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20will%20attract%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20planned%20to%20seal%20Haryana-Punjab%20borders%20to%20ensure%20protesting%20farmers%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20cannot%20enter%20Haryana%20before%20proceeding%20to%20Delhi.%20This%20move%20will%20inconvenience%20those%20travelling%20between%20Chandigarh%20and%20Delhi.%20Police%20have%20announced%20alternative%20routes%20for%20this%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20Police%20have%20advised%20commuters%20to%20avoid%20arterial%20roads%20on%20Tuesday.%20It%20has%20also%20warned%20of%20traffic%20disruption%20due%20to%20the%20protest.%20On%20the%20borders%20between%20Haryana%20and%20Delhi%2C%20cement%20barriers%2C%20barbed%20wires%20and%20sandbags%20are%20in%20place%20to%20stop%20the%20farmers%20from%20crossing%20into%20the%20national%20capital.%20Water%20cannons%20and%20drones%20have%20also%20been%20brought%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty%20companies%20of%20paramilitary%20forces%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20assist%20Haryana%20Police.%20Haryana%20police%20chief%20Shatrujeet%20Kapur%20warned%20of%20taking%20strict%20action%20if%20anyone%20tries%20to%20disrupt%20peace.%20The%20police%20have%20asked%20farmers%20to%20stay%20away%20and%20also%20warned%20of%20action%20if%20public%20property%20is%20damaged.%20Haryana%20Home%20Minister%20Anil%20Vij%2C%20too%2C%20has%20said%20the%20state%20government%20%26quot%3Bwill%20ensure%20complete%20peace%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20invited%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20for%20talks%20tomorrow.%20But%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20the%20meeting%20will%20result%20in%20the%20farmers%20calling%20off%20protests%20because%20the%20demands%20require%20detailed%20discussion%20and%20parliamentary%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20is%20being%20organised%20by%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%20and%20several%20farmers'%20organisations%20have%20distanced%20itself%20from%20it.%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Lakhowal)%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20in%202020-21%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Centre%20withdrawing%20three%20laws%2C%20said%20they%20won't%20join%20Tuesday's%20protest.%20Instead%2C%20they%20will%20participate%20in%20a%20protest%20on%20Friday.%20The%20BKU%2C%20however%2C%20warned%20that%20if%20farmers%20part%20of%20Tuesday's%20protest%20are%20%26quot%3Bmanhandled%26quot%3B%2C%20all%20unions%20will%20hit%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707638700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2gka4fi8_haryana-border_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-mobile-internet-off-barriers-ready-haryana-preps-to-stop-farmers-march-5035469%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mobile%20internet%20connectivity%20has%20been%20suspended%20in%20seven%20districts%20as%20the%20BJP-led%20Haryana%20government%20gears%20up%20to%20block%20the%20farmers'%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20Tuesday%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-mobile-internet-off-barriers-ready-haryana-preps-to-stop-farmers-march-5035469%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-mobile-internet-off-barriers-ready-haryana-preps-to-stop-farmers-march-5035469%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmers-protest-haryana-police-mobile-internet-off-barriers-ready-haryana-preps-to-stop-farmers