e%2C%20describing%20how%20this%20might%20affect%20the%20climate%2C%20different%20ecosystems%2C%20and%20civilisational%20infrastructures%20now%20and%20in%20the%20future.%20They%20outline%20a%20range%20of%20theoretical%20scenarios%20to%20guide%20governments%20and%20other%20institutions%20as%20they%20set%20targets%20to%20reduce%20fossil%20fuel%20burning%2C%20forest%20and%20wetland%20degradation%2C%20and%20other%20activities%20that%20directly%20contribute%20to%20the%20accumulation%20of%20atmospheric%20GHGs.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.ch%2Fsite%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2022%2F06%2FSPM_version_report_LR.pdf%5C%22%3EThey%E2%80%99ve%20determined%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20that%20the%20average%20global%20temperature%20is%20likely%20to%20rise%20by%201.5%C2%BAC%20between%202030%E2%80%932053%2C%20relative%20to%20what%20it%20was%20before%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%20%E2%80%93%20a%20threshold%20nearly%20touched%20already%20in%202023%2C%20when%20the%20globe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwmo.int%2Fmedia%2Fnews%2Fwmo-confirms-2023-smashes-global-temperature-record%5C%22%3Ewarmed%20by%201.45%C2%BAC%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20quantifying%20and%20describing%20the%20extreme%20threats%20that%20lie%20beyond%20this%20temperature%20threshold.%20These%20findings%20have%20put%20pressure%20on%20governments%20to%20make%20pledges%20about%20lowering%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%20within%20their%20borders.%20Perhaps%20the%20IPCC%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20triumph%20is%20in%20helping%20to%20shift%20the%20global%20conversation%20on%20climate%20justice%20and%20equitability%2C%20finally%20establishing%20the%20need%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98loss%20and%20damage%20fund%2C%E2%80%99%20whereby%20wealthier%20nations%20%E2%80%93%20who%20have%20historically%20contributed%20the%20far%20greater%20share%20of%20GHGs%20already%20in%20the%20atmosphere%20%E2%80%93%20can%20help%20poorer%20nations%20adapt%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20deal%20with%20its%20mounting%20onslaughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPCC%20reports%20are%20meticulous%2C%20exhaustive%2C%20based%20on%20top-notch%20science%2C%20and%20essential%20to%20our%20understanding%20of%20how%20the%20climate%20and%20Earth-system%20work.%20Running%20into%20thousands%20of%20pages%2C%20the%20reports%20are%20valiantly%20written%2C%20compiled%20by%20teams%20of%20earnest%20scientists%20and%20subject%20matter%20experts%20across%20a%20range%20of%20disciplines%20from%20around%20the%20globe.%20Yet%20despite%20this%20tremendous%20effort%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwedocs.unep.org%2Fbitstream%2Fhandle%2F20.500.11822%2F40932%2FEGR2022_ESEN.pdf%3Fsequence%3D8%5C%22%3Egovernments%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unep.org%2Fnews-and-stories%2Fpress-release%2Fnations-must-go-further-current-paris-pledges-or-face-global-warming%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNairobi%2C%2525252020%25252520November%252525202023%25252520%252525E2%25252580%25252593%25252520As%2Cpre-industrial%25252520levels%25252520this%25252520century%2C%5C%22%3Ewavering%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20their%20emissions%20reduction%20commitments%20and%20reneging%20on%20their%20contributions%20to%20the%20loss%20and%20damage%20fund.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20world%20is%20screaming%20right%20past%20the%20IPCC%E2%80%99s%20recommended%20warming%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%20during%20the%20nearly%20three%20decades%20that%20the%20IPCC%E2%80%99s%20heroic%20work%20has%20been%20ongoing%2C%20GHG%20emissions%20have%20only%20risen%20steadily.%20About%20half%20of%20the%20excess%20carbon-dioxide%20in%20the%20atmosphere%20today%20has%20accumulated%20only%20since%20%3Cem%3Eafter%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20IPCC%20began%20convening.%20Despite%20the%20boom%20in%20solar%20panels%20and%20windmills%20and%20the%20rising%20adoption%20of%20electric%20cars%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Erate%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20global%20GHG%20emissions%2C%20on%20average%2C%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiea.blob.core.windows.net%2Fassets%2F3c8fa115-35c4-4474-b237-1b00424c8844%2FCO2Emissionsin2022.pdf%5C%22%3Ekeeps%20rising%3C%2Fa%3E%20year%20after%20year%2C%20putting%20us%20currently%20on%20track%20to%20heat%20the%20planet%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB4zt-jZ4_CQ%5C%22%3E3%C2%BAC%20by%202100%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Despite%20growing%20global%20concern%20and%20expectation%20that%20Someone%20Needs%20To%20Figure%20This%20Out%20And%20Fix%20It%2C%20no%20one%E2%80%99s%20been%20able%20to%20effectively%20alter%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20course%20of%20warming.%20The%20situation%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20is%20deteriorating%20ever%20faster.%20Why%3F%20With%20all%20our%20sophisticated%20knowledge%20of%20atmospheric%20chemistry%20and%20dynamics%2C%20of%20winds%20and%20waters%20and%20solar%20radiation%2C%20of%20causes%20and%20effects%2C%20feedback%20loops%20and%20tipping%20points%E2%80%94what%20are%20we%20missing%3F%20Why%20are%20all%20our%20efforts%20still%20moving%20us%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20390px)%2085vw%2C%20390px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11112606%2FCoPs-v-CO2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22390%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11112606%2FCoPs-v-CO2.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11112606%2FCoPs-v-CO2-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11112606%2FCoPs-v-CO2-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696585%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22390%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDespite%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20attention%20and%20intention%20to%20curb%20global%20warming%2C%20while%20continuing%20with%20business-as-usual%20economic%20and%20industrial%20policies%2C%20led%20by%20international%20conferences%20and%20agreements%2C%20carbon%20dioxide%20has%20continued%20to%20accumulate%20in%20the%20atmosphere.%20Source%3A%20The%20Conversation%2FCC%20BY%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11113222%2FRising-CO2_Greenpeace.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22623%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11113222%2FRising-CO2_Greenpeace.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11113222%2FRising-CO2_Greenpeace-300x284.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11113222%2FRising-CO2_Greenpeace-1024x968.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696586%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22589%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20rate%20of%20atmospheric%20CO2%20accumulation%20(shown%20in%20parts%20per%20million%20(ppm))%20continues%20to%20accelerate.%20The%20rate%20slowed%20for%20only%20a%20few%20years%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20following%20enactment%20of%20the%20Montreal%20Protocols%2C%20which%20reduced%20the%20use%20of%20chemicals%20known%20to%20threaten%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20atmospheric%20ozone%20layer.%20Image%20credit%3A%20NOAA%2C%20chart%20by%20Barry%20Saxifrage%20at%20NationanalObserver.com%20and%20VisualCarbon.org%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20these%20dismal%20results%2C%20some%20people%20who%20have%20been%20tracking%20the%20climate%20crisis%20and%20its%20purported%20remedies%20are%20led%20to%20despair.%20Some%20conclude%20that%20human%20beings%20are%20incapable%20of%20living%20without%20destroying%20our%20world.%20But%20this%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20all%20evidence%20from%20the%20course%20of%20human%20evolution.%20People%20just%20like%20us%20have%20been%20around%20for%20nearly%20300%2C000%20years%20%E2%80%93%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20generations%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20depth%20and%20scale%20of%20global%20environmental%20disruptions%20never%20remotely%20began%20to%20approach%20anything%20like%20we%20face%20now%2C%20until%20perhaps%20ten%20generations%20ago%2C%20less%20than%20three%20hundred%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20changed%3F%20Is%20it%20simply%20human%20greed%2C%20as%20some%20say%3F%20Our%20selfishness%3F%20Apathy%3F%20These%20vices%20have%20certainly%20always%20been%20part%20of%20the%20human%20mix%20and%20no%20doubt%20play%20a%20role%20in%20stymying%20helpful%20responses%20to%20our%20crises.%20But%20why%20did%20it%20take%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20years%20for%20these%20ancient%20traits%20to%20emerge%20as%20fatal%20flaws%3F%20Simplifying%20the%20causes%20of%20our%20complex%20predicament%20to%20a%20few%20of%20the%20worst%20human%20traits%20is%20an%20overly%20narrow%20framing%20of%20the%20problems%20we%20face.%20It%20can%20be%20a%20way%20of%20shifting%20blame%20onto%20a%20small%20coterie%20of%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20the%20heads%20of%20oil%20companies%20or%20political%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20as%20an%20easy%20target%20for%20our%20anger%20or%20unease.%20But%20none%20of%20them%20created%20global%20warming.%20And%20while%20they%20may%20represent%20companies%20or%20groups%20who%20work%20against%20reducing%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20as%20individuals%20they%20cannot%20stop%20it.%20Their%20actions%20are%20legally%20and%20logistically%20constrained%20by%20the%20same%20systems%20that%20we%20depend%20upon%20for%20our%20modern%20livelihoods%3B%20their%20fossil-fuel%20products%20are%20the%20life-blood%20of%20the%20modern%20economy%20and%20their%20capitalist%20politics%20are%20its%20beating%20heart.%20Those%20CEOs%20and%20politicians%20are%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20merely%20today%E2%80%99s%20winners%20of%20the%20very%20same%20capitalist%20game%20that%20most%20of%20us%20are%20also%20playing%20to%20win%20at%2C%20whenever%20we%20hope%20to%20make%20more%20money%2C%20%E2%80%98get%20ahead%2C%E2%80%99%20or%20promote%20economic%20growth.%20Individual%20blame-mongering%20that%20glosses%20over%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20system%20we%E2%80%99re%20all%20a%20part%20of%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20most%20of%20us%20earnestly%20vote%20for%20%E2%80%93%20leads%20to%20useless%20or%20even%20dangerous%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114756%2FS2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221119%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114756%2FS2.png%201119w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114756%2FS2-300x98.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11114756%2FS2-1024x336.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696589%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22367%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20understand%20that%20how%20we%20frame%20a%20problem%20directs%20where%20we%20look%20for%20answers%2C%20right%20or%20wrong%20%E2%80%93%20as%20in%20that%20old%20aphorism%20that%20when%20you%20only%20have%20a%20hammer%2C%20every%20problem%20looks%20like%20a%20nail.%20Or%20the%20apocryphal%20story%20of%20the%20guy%20searching%20for%20his%20keys%20under%20a%20streetlamp%2C%20though%20he%20could%E2%80%99ve%20lost%20them%20anywhere%3B%20%E2%80%98because%20this%20is%20where%20the%20light%20is%20good%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20explains.%20It%20matters%20very%20much%20how%20we%20frame%20the%20predicament%20we%20face%2C%20how%20we%20describe%20its%20causes%20and%20effects%2C%20how%20we%20conceive%20of%20responsibility%20and%20envisage%20justice.%20What%20if%20the%20reason%20our%20response%20to%20global%20warming%20has%20been%20ineffectual%20is%20because%20we%E2%80%99re%20asking%20the%20wrong%20questions%3F%20What%20if%20we%E2%80%99re%20framing%20the%20problem%20too%20narrowly%20%E2%80%93%20or%20looking%20entirely%20in%20the%20wrong%20place%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20take%20one%20example%2C%20consider%20that%20the%20presently%20privileged%20worldview%20describes%20our%20planetary%20system%20primarily%20in%20mechanistic%20terms%20and%20approaches%20every%20difficulty%20as%20a%20set%20of%20engineering%20problems%20to%20be%20optimally%20solved%20for%20furthering%20human%20economic%20growth%20in%20a%20capitalist%2C%20global%2C%20industrial%20economy.%20But%20what%20if%20we%20took%20a%20broader%20view%20grounded%20in%20an%20understanding%20of%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20living%20systems%3F%20The%20discipline%20of%20ecology%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20strives%20toward%20holism%2C%20rather%20than%20mechanism%2C%20in%20understanding%20our%20Earth-system.%20It%20was%20gaining%20prominence%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20but%20then%20quickly%20fell%20out%20of%20fashion%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20dismissed%20by%20many%20as%20too%20%E2%80%98soft%E2%80%99%20of%20a%20science%2C%20which%20might%20well%20be%20translated%20as%20%3Cem%3Enot%20a%20way%20to%20make%20money%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20mainstream%20responses%20to%20climate%20change%20seek%20to%20frame%20the%20problem%20in%20ways%20that%20can%20be%20answered%20by%20%E2%80%98market%20solutions.%E2%80%99%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20lens%20through%20which%20our%20institutions%20and%20global%20systems%20have%20learned%20to%20see%20all%20problems.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20sought%20to%20simplify%20and%20reduce%20the%20causes%20and%20consequences%20of%20climate%20change%20to%20technicalities%2C%20whether%20that%E2%80%99s%20temperature%20rise%2C%20sea-level%20rise%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20atmospheric%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20or%20some%20other%20individuated%20metric.%20They%20then%20envision%20technical%20%E2%80%98fixes%E2%80%99%20to%20these%20problems.%20But%20our%20changing%20climate%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20merely%20present%20a%20set%20of%20operational%20parameters%20to%20be%20tweaked.%20We%20are%20facing%20a%20fundamental%20revision%20of%20the%20entire%20Earth-system%2C%20a%20dramatic%20shift%20away%20from%20the%20state%20it%20had%20inhabited%20since%20long%20before%20the%20dawn%20of%20human%20civilisation%20toward%20a%20new%20and%20unknown%20state%20for%20the%20future.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20about%20rising%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20but%20a%20degraded%20biosphere%2C%20alterations%20in%20the%20water%20and%20nitrogen%20cycles%2C%20and%20other%20derangements%20%E2%80%93%20in%20fact%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stockholmresilience.org%2F5.3d04209a18a2642b2fc162a3.html%5C%22%3Eexceeded%20six%20of%20the%20nine%3C%2Fa%3E%20known%20planetary%20boundaries%20for%20civilizational%20stability.%20And%20we%E2%80%99re%20driving%20these%20destabilising%20changes%20by%20the%20way%20we%20live%2C%20through%20the%20very%20structures%20and%20dynamics%20of%20the%20vaunted%20civilisation%20we%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20preserve.%20Both%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20ecological%20degradation%20caused%20by%20our%20civilisation%20and%20our%20responses%20to%20it%20will%20affect%20the%20future%20of%20all%20life%20on%20Earth%3A%20The%20stakes%20are%20literally%20existential.%20We%20must%20respond%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20effectively%20address%20this%20ecocide%2C%20we%20need%20to%20change%20the%20way%20we%20live%20%E2%80%93%20the%20way%20our%20global%20civilisation%20is%20structured.%20Yet%20billions%20of%20lives%20are%20dependent%20upon%20%3Cem%3Emaintaining%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20present%20systems.%20Drastically%20altering%20patterns%20of%20production%20or%20consumption%20puts%20everybody%20within%20this%20civilisation%20at%20risk.%20This%20makes%20what%20we%20face%20not%20just%20a%20%3Cem%3Eset%20of%20problems%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20a%20%3Cem%3Epredicament.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Problems%20may%20have%20solutions.%20Predicaments%20do%20not.%20Predicaments%2C%20at%20best%2C%20can%20be%20met%20with%20resp