ies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20a%20collection%20of%2020%2C000%20crore%20'Sitaram'%20booklets%20from%20the%20devotees%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Punit%20Ram%20Das%20Maharaj%2C%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20bank%2C%20the%20number%20of%20daily%20visitors%20at%20the%20bank%20has%20increased%20after%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20grand%20temple%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bank%20provides%20free%20booklets%20and%20red%20pens%20to%20devotees%20and%20keeps%20track%20of%20each%20account.%20One%20has%20to%20write%20'Sitaram'%20at%20least%205%20lakh%20times%20to%20get%20an%20account%20opened%20in%20the%20bank%20and%20then%20a%20passbook%20is%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20136%20branches%20of%20the%20bank%20across%20India%20and%20even%20abroad.%20The%20account%20holders%20also%20send%20us%20the%20booklets%20by%20post%20and%20we%20maintain%20the%20ledger%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Puneet%20Ram%20Das%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20visitors%20also%20question%20the%20benefits%20of%20writing%20Sitaram%20and%20depositing%20it%20into%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tell%20them%20that%20the%20way%20we%20visit%20temples%20of%20gods%20and%20goddesses%20for%20inner%20peace%2C%20faith%20and%20virtue%2C%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20writing%20'Sitaram'%20and%20depositing%20the%20same%20into%20the%20bank%20is%20a%20form%20of%20a%20prayer.%20Don't%20we%20say%20that%20God%20has%20his%20own%20account%20of%20everyone's%20good%20and%20bad%20deeds%3F%20This%20is%20something%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20devotees%20find%20solace%20and%20profound%20spiritual%20enrichment%20in%20writing%2C%20chanting%20and%20reminiscing%20Lord%20Ram's%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPuneet%20Ram%20Das%20explained%20that%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20by%20writing%20the%20name%2084%20lakh%20times%2C%20one%20can%20attain%20'Moksha'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeetu%20Nagar%2C%20from%20Gaya%20in%20Bihar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20visiting%20the%20bank%20for%2014%20years%2C%20said%20this%20is%20his%20only%20form%20of%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20praying%20at%20a%20temple%2C%20I%20practise%20this%20and%20it%20has%20always%20worked%20for%20me%20whenever%20I%20have%20felt%20low%20or%20have%20been%20in%20trouble.%20I%20write%20it%20throughout%20the%20year%20and%20deposit%20at%20the%20bank%20once%20a%20year.%20There%20is%20an%20option%20to%20send%20by%20post%20too%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20to%20visit%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagar%20said%20he%20has%20already%20deposited%20booklets%20with%20a%20name%20count%20of%201.37%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuman%20Das%2C%20another%20account%20holder%20from%20Bareily%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20said%2C%20said%20he%20has%20written%20'Sitaram'%2025%20lakh%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20told%20my%20neighbour%20about%20the%20bank%2C%20he%20thought%20I%20must%20be%20crazy%20but%20I%20have%20strong%20belief.%20Whenever%20I%20do%20the%20writing%2C%20I%20feel%20my%20prayers%20are%20being%20heard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20consecrated%20at%20the%20grand%20temple%20in%20a%20consecration%20ceremony%20on%20January%2022%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Lakhs%20of%20people%20watched%20the%20%26quot%3Bpran%20pratishtha%20(consecration)%26quot%3B%20ceremony%20on%20television%20in%20their%20homes%20and%20neighbourhood%20temples%2C%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20historic%20event%20held%20just%20months%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707634080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fclvrptp8_ayodhya_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%