srupted%20Education%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohan%20had%20begun%20the%20book%20with%20a%20rich%20account%20of%20children%20from%20low-income%20households%20in%20heartland%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20besotted%20by%20a%20phone-screen%20teaching%20them%20elementary%20mathematics.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20this%20image%20is%20true%20%E2%80%93%20and%20yet%2C%20learning%20has%20many%20dimensions%20beyond%20this%20image.%20Learning%20is%20equally%20about%20peers%20and%20authority%20figures.%20This%20is%20especially%20true%20of%20disciplines%20like%20the%20social%20sciences%20and%20the%20humanities%3B%20and%20even%20higher-level%20mathematics%20or%20the%20sciences%20or%20professional%20streams%20need%20peer%20discussion%20at%20several%20crucial%20levels%20of%20the%20value%20chain.%20One%20only%20risks%20entrenching%20poor%20student%20teacher%20ratios%20(in%20school%20and%20university)%20through%20the%20excuse%20of%20technology%20developed%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20firms%20%E2%80%93%20this%20can%20be%20a%20vicious%20cycle%20allowing%20education%20to%20slip%20into%20a%20spiral%20of%20children%20on%20screens%20with%20%E2%80%9Ceducation%E2%80%9D%20being%20beamed%20down%20from%20ever-more%20centralised%20entities%20or%20apps.%20This%20is%20already%20the%20case%20with%20the%20handful%20of%20centralised%20Boards%20running%20Indian%20education%20with%20narrow%20%E2%80%9Cobjective%E2%80%9D%20ideas%20of%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20303px)%2085vw%2C%20303px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11115740%2F614FZPLQC3L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22303%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11115740%2F614FZPLQC3L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20626w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11115740%2F614FZPLQC3L._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-188x300.jpg%20188w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696593%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22484%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EArjun%20Mohan%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EEducating%20a%20Billion%3A%20How%20Edtech%20Startups%2C%20Apps%2C%20Youtube%20and%20AI%20Disrupted%20Education%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EPenguin%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20Mohan%20is%20simplistic%20when%20he%20repeats%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Creal%20problem%20is%20of%20quality%20of%20delivery%E2%80%9D.%20Centralisation%20risks%20making%20cogs%20of%20both%20student%20and%20teacher%20%E2%80%93%20instead%20of%20empowering%20student(s)%20and%20teacher%20in%20small%2C%20vibrant%2C%20discussion-packed%20classrooms%20where%20the%20light%20bulb%20repeated%20goes%20off%20in%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20head%20as%20they%20discover%20the%20magic%20of%20both%20learning%20of%2C%20as%20well%20as%20participating%20in%2C%20the%20tangible%2C%20nurturing%20world%20of%20the%20classroom.%20Despite%20millions%20of%20parents%20spending%20lakhs%20in%20several%20private%20schools%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20how%20much%20a%20student%20can%20learn%20and%20retain%20when%20what%20is%20tested%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20are%20chiefly%20in%20the%20form%20of%20multiple%20choice.%20Much%20of%20the%20excitement%20of%20the%20classroom%20is%20simply%20forgotten%2C%20and%20indeed%20the%20evaluation%20systems%2Fexams%20are%20complicit%20in%20the%20destruction%20of%20this%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohan%20is%20unquestioning%20in%20his%20regard%20for%20the%20current%20test%20preparation%20industry%2C%20which%20is%20all%20about%20hacks%20and%20shortcuts%2C%20%E2%80%9Ccracking%E2%80%9D%20exams%20and%20boot%20camps%20and%20demo%20sessions.%20He%20vividly%20describes%20this%20underworld%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20education%20system%2C%20and%20the%20undoubtedly%20hard%20work%20he%20and%20his%20team%20put%20in%20travelling%20the%20breadth%20of%20many%20states%2C%20recruiting%20teachers%2C%20recording%20and%20editing%20videos%20through%20the%20night%2C%20and%20building%20distribution%20in%20remote%20corners%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20book%20captures%20well%20the%20feverish%20headiness%20of%20start-up%20life%20as%20they%20unfold%20in%20waves%20in%20the%20edtech%20sector%20from%20the%20nineties%20onward%20%E2%80%93%20these%20are%20indeed%20the%20best%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20price%20one%20pays%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccracking%E2%80%9D%20exams%20with%20only%20exam-oriented%20knowledge%20is%20steep%20because%20much%20of%20college%20will%20now%20be%20spent%20unlearning%20this%20and%20actually%20learning%20to%20learn.%20Many%20students%20are%20simply%20unable%20to%20make%20this%20transition%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20this%20is%20certainly%20a%20factor%20in%20the%20endemically%20poor%20mental%20health%20of%20students%20in%20Indian%20universities.%20Students%20grown%20up%20in%20a%20purely%20test%20preparation%20mode%20are%20unable%20to%20think%20beyond%20multiple%20choice%20and%20write%20lengthier%20qualitative%20answers%20which%20emphasise%20innovation%20of%20response%20rather%20than%20a%20generic%20%E2%80%9Ccorrect%20answer%E2%80%9D.%20It%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20even%20in%20the%20sciences%2C%20the%20true%20scientist%20or%20engineer%20is%20she%20who%20pushes%20knowledge%20to%20new%20boundaries%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20more%20important%20is%20to%20learn%20to%20ask%20the%20right%20questions%2C%20not%20so%20much%20to%20get%20a%20pre-decided%20and%20common%20right%20answer.%20The%20idea%20of%20the%20hack%20or%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20fetish%20India%20must%20outgrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20media%20and%20coaching%20institutes%20fete%20these%20toppers%2C%20because%20this%20gives%20a%20sense%20that%20this%20is%20intellectual%20achievement%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20an%20exam-taking%20achievement.%20Mohan%20takes%20this%20world%20of%20education%20as%20a%20given%2C%20sharing%20his%20own%20struggles%20with%20his%20CAT%20grades.%20While%20his%20story%20may%20be%20personally%20inspiring%20(small-town%20boy%20receiving%20multiple%20IIM%20offers)%2C%20the%20book%20gives%20little%20sense%20of%20the%20cost%20that%20the%20larger%20educational%20ecology%20pays.%20This%20is%20why%20at%20the%20university%20level%20India%20struggles%20so%20hard%20to%20do%20well%20in%20international-quality%20research%20%E2%80%93%20students%20fed%20on%20a%20diet%20of%20hacks%20must%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20college%20years%20having%20to%20re-learn%20how%20to%20think%20in%20a%20more%20open-ended%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20start-ups%2Ftechnologies%2Fapps%20often%20feeding%20on%20the%20insecurities%20of%20students%20from%20smaller%20towns%2C%20or%20lower-income%20families%2C%20where%20there%20is%20already%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20pervasive%20failure%20of%20private%20and%20public%20education%2C%20and%20the%20feeling%20that%20education%20as%20social%20mobility%20is%20a%20lost%20myth.%20Thus%2C%20the%20syllabus%20of%20competitive%20exams%20are%20taken%20as%20a%20given%2C%20instead%20of%20just%20as%20a%20convention%20agreed%20by%20some%20opaque%20process%20%E2%80%93%20again%2C%20for%20this%20lack%20of%20accountability%20in%20syllabus-design%20India%20pays%20the%20price%20with%20its%20poorly%20employable%20youth.%20A%20small%20shift%20of%20syllabus%20%E2%80%93%20in%20terms%20of%20content%2C%20or%20time%20or%20answer%20mode%20%E2%80%93%20and%20all%20these%20paltry%20hacks%20will%20crumble%20in%20the%20dust.%20And%20it%20is%20such%20shifts%20that%20occur%20in%20the%20real%20world%20while%20the%20world%20of%20entrance%20exams%20give%20a%20false%20illusion%20of%20learning%20and%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20225px)%2085vw%2C%20225px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11120918%2Fdownload-21.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22225%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11120918%2Fdownload-21.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11120918%2Fdownload-21-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696594%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22225%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EArjun%20Mohan.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40_arjunmohan_%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20in%20a%20good%20system%20geared%20toward%20the%20real%20world%2C%20the%20syllabus%20and%20evaluation%20(be%20it%20NEET%20or%20CBSE)%20should%20anyway%20evolve%20every%20year%20to%20accommodate%20constant%20new%20knowledge%20and%20increasing%20uncertainty.%20This%20itself%20will%20force%20the%20coaching%20institutes%20to%20teach%20with%20depth%20and%20range%2C%20and%20not%20with%20just%20a%20view%20to%20sales.%20The%20hacks%20can%20be%20left%20to%20marketing%20%E2%80%93%20Mohan%20has%20several%20interesting%20nuggets%20on%20consumer%20behaviour%20such%20as%20youngsters%20in%20small%20towns%20being%20forced%20to%20access%20parent%E2%80%99s%20cell%20phone%20in%20front%20of%20them%20and%20only%20when%20the%20latter%20were%20preoccupied%20watching%20television!%20But%20such%20insights%20into%20the%20behavioural%20use%20of%20smartphones%20should%20be%20used%20to%20design%20policy%20and%20pedagogy%2C%20not%20to%20calculate%20the%20ideal%20time%20when%20the%20sales%20rep%20should%20invade%20the%20parent%E2%80%99s%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20gives%20us%20a%20good%20sense%20of%20the%20educational%20landscape%20and%20the%20possibilities%20of%20digitisation%20and%20online%20learning%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20there%20is%20enormous%20potential%2C%20and%20that%20India%20has%20to%20get%20this%20right.%20What%20one%20might%20want%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20though%20is%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20industry%20is%20not%20simply%20parasitic%20and%20exploitative%20of%20the%20worst%20of%20the%20beleaguered%20school%20system.%20Instead%2C%20the%20vigilant%20hope%20should%20be%20that%20technologies%20supplement%20the%20schools%20and%20universities%20by%20furthering%20motivation%2C%20by%20helping%20disadvantaged%20students%2C%20by%20charting%20pathways%20and%20networks%20for%20gifted%20students%2C%20by%20multiplying%20meaningful%20forms%20of%20evaluations%20and%20admission%20beyond%20poorly%20designed%20exams%2C%20by%20improving%20writing%20and%20communication%20skills%2C%20%C2%A0by%20engendering%20new%20formats%20of%20output%20that%20are%20in%20line%20with%20true%20research%20and%20alternative%20career%20paths.%20If%20the%20industry%20manages%20even%20a%20fraction%20of%20all%20this%20over%20the%20coming%20decade%20%E2%80%93%20with%20patience%20and%20reflection%20instead%20of%20frenzy%20%E2%80%93%20India%20does%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20actually%20%E2%80%9Ceducate%E2%80%9D%20the%20billion%20that%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20title%20refers%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENikhil%20Govind%20is%20Professor%20and%20Head%20of%20the%20Manipal%20Centre%20for%20Humanities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707633884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F02163135%2F22511851655_9a13f28bd0_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Farjun-mohan-educating-a-billion%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arjun%20Mohan's%20book%20captures%20well%20the%20feverish%20headiness%20of%20start-up%20life%20as%20they%20unfold%20in%20waves%20in%20the%20edtech%20sector%20from%20the%20nineties%20onward.%20What%20one%20might%20want%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20though%20is%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20industry%20is%20not%20simply%20parasitic%20and%20exploitative%20of%20the%20worst%20of%20the%20beleaguered%20school%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Farjun-mohan-educating-a-billion%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karan%20says%20he%20is%20going%20through%20a%20'purple%20patch'%22%2C%22co