tprints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Taylor%20Swift's%20attorney%20has%20said%20that%20if%20Mr%20Sweeney%20continues%20to%20publish%20information%20tracking%20her%20jet%20travels%2C%20%E2%80%9Cshe%20will%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20pursue%20any%20legal%20remedies%20available%20to%20her%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F02%2F06%2Ftech%2Ftaylor-swift-private-jet-tracker%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20letter%20by%20Ms%20Morrone%20accuses%20Mr%20Sweeney%20of%20disregarding%20the%20public%20safety%20of%20others%20%26quot%3Bin%20exchange%20for%20public%20attention%20and%2For%20requests%20for%20financial%20gain%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20even%20references%20Elon%20Musk%20offering%20Mr%20Sweeney%20%245%2C000%20to%20delete%20the%20Twitter%20account%20tracking%20his%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20this%20letter%2C%20the%2021-year-old%20has%20said%20he%20never%20intended%20any%20harm%20with%20his%20actions%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20is%20compiling%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20information%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20actually%20think%20Swift%20has%20some%20good%20songs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20college%20student%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20in%20transparency%20and%20public%20information.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707633540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2l87cibo_jack-sweeney_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-jack-sweeney-the-jet-tracker-who-angers-taylor-swift-elon-musk-5035774%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pop%20sensation%20Taylor%20Swift's%20attorneys%20have%20threatened%20legal%20action%20against%20Jack%20Sweeney%2C%20a%20student%20who%20tracks%20private%20jets%20of%20celebrities%2C%20including%20that%20of%20the%20Blank%20Space%20hitmaker.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22ca