his%20writer-contributors.%20He%20was%20acutely%20aware%20of%20the%20unfairness%20of%20the%20situation.%20As%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Progressive%20Writers'%20Association%20and%20a%20proponent%20of%20Communism%2C%20Sahir%20earned%20a%20reputation%20that%20went%20beyond%20his%20literary%20genius.%20But%20the%20late%201940s%20were%20dangerous%20years%20for%20any%20%3Cem%3Esurkha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20literally%20meaning%20'Red-coloured'%2C%20intellectual.%20The%20government%20of%20Pakistan%20was%20too%20eager%20to%20put%20this%20young%20poet%20behind%20bars.%20Sahir%20fled%20to%20Delhi%20and%20carried%20some%20trauma%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%2C%20playing%20Sahir%20in%20the%20play%2C%20brings%20out%20all%20the%20poet's%20struggles%20through%20his%20powerful%2C%20personalised%20storytelling.%20Never%20leaving%20the%20character%2C%20he%20often%20breaks%20the%20fourth%20wall%20to%20address%20the%20audience.%20That%20his%20words-Sahir's%20words-seemingly%20address%20the%20audience%20of%20today%20is%20a%20function%20of%20Sahir's%20eternal%20relevance.%20As%20long%20as%20there%20is%20inequality%20in%20the%20world%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20Sahir%20verse%20addressing%2C%20highlighting%20it.%20On%20top%20of%20it%2C%20Danish's%20own%20poetic%20sensibility%2C%20complete%20with%20his%20politics%2C%20adds%20a%20distinct%20flavour%20to%20Sahir's%20words%20even%20almost%2045%20years%20after%20the%20latter's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahir%20has%20often%20been%20straitjacketed%20as%20the%20poet%20of%20despondency%20and%20melancholia%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20eternal%20lyrics%20for%20films%20like%20Pyasa.%20A%20contemporary%20of%20Faiz%20Ahmed%20Faiz%2C%20he%2C%20too%2C%20has%20an%20answer%20to%20this%20charge.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EHam%20ghamzada%20hain%3Cbr%3E%5CnLaayen%20kahan%20se%20khushi%20ke%20geet%2C%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnDenge%20wohijo%20paayenge%20is%20zindagi%20se%20ham%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Faiz%2C%20his%20poetry%2C%20too%2C%20is%20not%20created%20in%20a%20vacuum%3B%20cultural%20materialism%20informs%20both%20the%20poets.%20And%20it%20informs%20the%20art%20of%20poet-performer%20Danish%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Danish%20Husain%20in%20Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Danish%20Husain%20in%20Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fo2k20p5_danish_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%20Husain%20in%20'Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun'%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Nishtha%20Gautam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20events%20and%20verses%20to%20weave%20together%20Sahir's%20biography%20is%20a%20clear%20testimony%20of%20Danish's%20indictment%20of%20communalism%2C%20hierarchy-driven%20literary%20world%2C%20gender%20inequality%2C%20populism%2C%20class%20inequities%2C%20hypocritical%20politics%20of%20the%20day%2C%20and%20the%20marginal%20status%20of%20artistic%20genius%20in%20the%20commercial%20enterprise%20of%20filmmaking.%20Danish%2C%20it%20appears%2C%20uses%20Sahir's%20words%20to%20express%20his%20own%20dissatisfactions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EOn%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Sahir%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%3Cem%3E%20Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20dramatic%20thrust%20is%20on%20the%20ebbs%20and%20tides%20of%20Sahir's%20personal%20and%20professional%20life-both%20going%20back%20to%20his%20mother%20through%20an%20invisible%20umbilical%20cord%20that%20he%20could%20never%20detach.%20Sahir's%20deep%20attachment%20with%20and%20respect%20for%20his%20mother%20became%20a%20leitmotif%20for%20all%20his%20relationships%20with%20women.%20A%20vocal%20advocate%20of%20women's%20rights%2C%20Sahir's%20feminism%20perhaps%20came%20with%20a%20hefty%20price%20tag.%20None%20of%20his%20romantic%20relationships%20survived%20his%20radical%20attitudes.%20He%20was%20not%20the%20man%20to%20challenge%20the%20choices%20his%20women%20made%2C%20especially%20when%20his%20emotional%20limitations%20disallowed%20any%20blossoming%20of%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20Sahir's%20love%20poetry%20is%20as%20powerful%20as%20his%20'social-cause'%20verses.%20The%20play%20makes%20use%20of%20some%20of%20his%20best-known%20verses%20written%20for%20Hindi%20cinema%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3EJaane%20Kya%20Tune%20Kahi%2C%20Kabhi%20Kabhi%20Mere%20Dil%20Mein%2C%20and%20Abhi%20Na%20Jaao%20Chhodkar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20important%20thing%20about%20Sahir's%20love%20poetry%20is%20the%20beloved's%20positioning%20as%20an%20equal%20partner.%20She's%20neither%20a%20coy%20mistress%20nor%20the%20lady-on-a-high-pedestal%20of%20the%20courtly%20love%20tradition.%20Unrequited%20and%20unconsummated%2C%20Sahir's%20love%20moves%20and%20revels%20in%20unchartered%20territory.%20This%20reviewer%20feels%20that%20the%20inclusion%20of%20'%3Cem%3EChalo%20Ek%20Baar%20Phir%20Se%20Ajnabi%20Ban%20Jaye%20Hum%20Dono%3C%2Fem%3E'%20in%20the%20play%20would%20have%20reinforced%20this%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20theatre%20festival%20of%20the%20National%20School%20of%20Drama%20this%20year%20opens%20with%20%3Cem%3EMain%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun%3C%2Fem%3E.%20After%20houseful%20shows%20at%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20the%20Performing%20Arts%20(NCPA)%20and%20the%20Prithvi%20Theatre%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20this%20will%20be%20Danish's%20first%20outing%20in%20Delhi%20as%20Sahir.%20Javed%20Akhtar%20was%20a%20much%20younger%20colleague%20of%20Sahir%20in%20the%20worlds%20of%20cinema%20and%20Urdu%20poetry.%20They%20were%20also%20close%20friends.%20Sahir's%20influence%20is%20writ%20large%20in%20Javed%20Akhtar's%20poetry%20of%20resistance%20and%20rebelliousness.%20Danish%2C%20a%20much%20younger%20poet%2C%20has%20not%20had%20the%20same%20fortune.%20But%20he%20has%20found%20a%20way%20to%20claim%20Sahir's%20legacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%20becomes%20Sahir.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707628020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fiuobvf3g_danish_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhen-urdu-poet-sahir-surkha-ludhianvi-met-danish-daastaango-5035430%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20'Main%20Pal%20Do%20Pal%20Ka%20Shaayar%20Hun'%2C%20which%20opens%20this%20year's%20theatre%20festival%20of%20the%20National%20School%20of%20Drama%2C%20actor-playwright-director%20Danish%20Husain%20gives%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi-the%20man%20an%20edge%20over%20Sahir-the%20poet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhen-urdu-poet-sahir-surkha-ludhianvi-met-danish-daastaango-5035430%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhen-urdu-poet-sahir-surkha-ludhianvi-met-danish-daastaango-5035430%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhen-urdu-poet-sahir-surkha-ludhianvi-met-danish-daastaango-5035430%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20says%20he%20would%20'encourage'%20Russia%20to%20attack%20Nato%20allies%20who%20do%20not%20pay%20their%20bills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707628008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA065%2Fproduction%2F_132616014_5efbc8e1d76bf6b38ebb124c8e961b8ffd5da7fd0_171_3065_17231000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68266447%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20presidential%20hopeful%20says%20he%20would%20not%20protect%20any%20country%20failing%20to%20pay%20its%20bills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1725%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68266447%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68266447.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68266447.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Politics%20Bounces%20Back%20in%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25140239%2FPakistan-elections.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20dust%20settles%20on%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20recently%20concluded%20elections%2C%20some%20underlying%20facts%20will%20come%20into%20clearer%20focus%2C%20namely%20the%20further%20entrenchment%20of%20devolved%20and%20accommodative%20democratic%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20first%20the%20dust.%20The%20resilience%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaaf%20(PTI)%20is%2C%20obviously%20enough%2C%20the%20big%20story.%20After%20he%20had%20fallen%20out%20with%20his%20former%20mentors%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20%E2%80%98establishment%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20euphemism%20for%20the%20armed%20forces%E2%80%99%20extra-constitutional%20political%20power%20%E2%80%93%20he%20ended%20up%20in%20detention%2C%20and%20his%20party%20was%20put%20under%20legal%20and%20extra-legal%20pressures.%20In%20what%20became%20a%20test%20of%20their%20organisational%20ability%2C%20the%20party%20was%20unable%20to%20retain%20a%20unified%20election%20symbol%20and%20its%20nominees%20were%20forced%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%20as%20independent%20candidates.%20Despite%20these%20disadvantages%20and%20of%20course%2C%20the%20absence%20from%20the%20campaign%20of%20its%20popular%20leader%2C%20PTI%20managed%20to%20win%20more%20seats%20than%20any%20other%20party%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20and%20got%20a%20landslide%20majority%20in%20the%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20province.%20It%20also%20went%20neck%20and%20neck%20with%20Nawaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(N)%20in%20the%20most%20populous%20Punjab%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20supporters%20who%20are%20prone%20to%20grandiose%20historical%20comparisons%20are%20incorrect%20in%20claiming%20that%20either%20their%20persecution%20or%20their%20performance%20was%20unprecedented.%20Claims%20of%20bias%20are%20valid%20but%20do%20not%20amount%20to%20egregious%20deviations%20from%20past%20practice.%20The%20violence%20unleashed%20by%20the%20Musharraf%20regime%20and%20its%20alleged%20collaborators%20before%20the%202008%20elections%20against%20its%20opponents%20claimed%20hundreds%20of%20lives%20including%20that%20of%20Benazir%20Bhutto.%20In%20the%202013%20elections%20Tehreek-e-Taliban%20Pakistan%20(TTP)%20selectively%20threatened%20and%20then%20attacked%20campaigns%20of%20three%20parties%20(PPP%2C%20ANP%20and%20MQM)%2C%20murdering%20party%20supporters%20and%20kidnapping%20the%20son%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Yusuf%20Raza%20Gillani%20from%20a%20campaign%20event.%20The%20persecution%20of%20PMLN%20leaders%20and%20candidates%20in%202018%20was%2C%20arguably%2C%20no%20less%20severe%20than%20what%20PTI%20faced%20this%20time%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20defiance%20and%20%E2%80%98bounce%E2%80%99%20are%20also%20not%20unprecedented.%20The%20PPP%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20its%20charismatic%20leader%20went%20on%20to%20fight%20and%20win%20the%202008%20elections%20on%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%9Cdemocracy%20is%20the%20best%20revenge%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20the%20PMLN%20made%20a%20good%20showing%20in%202018%20on%20the%20chant%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Evote%20ko%20izzat%20do%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Crespect%20the%20vote%E2%80%9D.%20PTI%20joined%20the%20ranks%20of%20other%20parties%20when%20it%20too%20turned%20to%20the%20ballot%20as%20its%20primary%20form%20of%20protest%20calling%20for%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ezulm%20ka%20badla%3C%2Fem%3E%20vote%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cvote%20to%20avenge%20injustice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20comes%20next%20is%20complicated%20for%20both%20the%20PTI%20and%20the%20establishment.%20Khan%20would%20want%20to%20use%20the%20electoral%20resilience%20of%20his%20party%20to%20negotiate%20with%20the%20establishment%20for%20his%20way%20out%20of%20detention%20and%20court%20cases%2C%20and%20possibly%20back%20into%20office.%20But%20while%20the%20political%20wind%20might%20be%20with%20him%2C%20parliamentary%20arithmetic%20is%20not.%20According%20to%20results%20already%20published%20by%20the%20election%20commission%2C%20PTI%20supported%20independents%20would%20constitute%20the%20largest%20bloc%20in%20the%20national%20assembly%20but%20fall%20well%20short%20of%20an%20overall%20majority.%20PTI%20leaders%20claim%20that%20they%20have%20been%20cheated%20out%20of%20many%20seats%20and%20that%20if%20awarded%20they%20would%20have%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20national%20and%20Punjab%20assemblies.%20Some%2C%20though%20not%20all%2C%20such%20claims%20might%20be%20valid%2C%20but%20legal%20challenges%20to%20declared%20results%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20long%20drawn%20affairs%20with%20no%20guarantee%20of%20success.%20In%20the%20meanwhile%20parliamentary%20business%20will%20need%20to%20be%20attended%20to%2C%20and%20PMLN%20with%20somewhat%20fewer%20seats%20than%20PTI%2C%20but%20with%20ongoing%20relationships%20with%20other%20parties%20and%20non-PTI%20independents%2C%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20might%20be%20tempted%20to%20use%20the%20momentum%20of%20its%20election%20win%20to%20switch%20to%20protest%20mode%E2%80%93%20about%20election%20irregularities%20and%20then%20about%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20detention.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20fondness%20and%20ability%20to%20elevate%20his%20own%20person%20to%20a%20point%20of%20principle%20means%20that%20he%20might%20well%20demand%20this%20of%20his%20followers.%C2%A0%20One%20example%20of%20such%20audacity%20was%20the%20failed%20attempt%20at%20%E2%80%98insurrection%E2%80%99%20on%20May%209%2C%202023%20when%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20supporters%20staged%20violent%20attacks%20on%20state%20symbols%20and%20military%20facilities%20in%20protest%20against%20his%20detention%20in%20a%20court%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20Have%20the%20Pakistan%20Elections%20Made%20the%20Country%E2%80%99s%20Crisis%20Worse%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-have-the-pakistan-elections-made-the-countrys-crisis-worse%5C%22%3EHave%20the%20Pakistan%20Elections%20Made%20the%20Country%E2%80%99s%20Crisis%20Worse%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternatively%2C%20PTI%20winning%20candidates%20might%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20humdrum%20processes%20of%20parliamentary%20politics%2C%20while%20keeping%20up%20lip%20service%20about%20the%20plight%20of%20their%20detained%20leader.%20They%20have%20an%20incontrovertible%20claim%20to%20forming%20the%20provincial%20government%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20and%20would%20constitute%20a%20powerful%20opposition%20in%20Punjab%20and%20in%20Islamabad.%20Getting%20involved%20in%20parliamentary%20politics%20and%20in%20returning%20to%20office%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20would%20involve%20some%20level%20of%20autonomy%20from%20the%20whims%20of%20their%20popular%20leader.%20And%20it%20may%20expose%20them%20to%20fissures%20and%20factionalism.%20This%20process%20will%20start%20as%20soon%20as%20a%20few%20days%20from%20now%20when%20the%20PTI%20group%20will%20have%20to%20agree%20on%20parliamentary%20tactics%20and%20leadership%20positions%20nationally%20and%20in%20Punjab%2C%20and%20government%20formation%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conundrum%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98establishment%E2%80%99%20is%20no%20less%20complicated.%20The%20PTI%20was%20mentored%20into%20office%20in%202018%20to%20disrupt%20political%20accommodation%20between%20the%20PMLN%20and%20the%20PPP%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20encroaching%20upon%20the%20extra-constitutional%20powers%20of%20the%20establishment.%20Successive%20constitutional%20and%20legislative%20changes%20particularly%20the%2018th%20Constitutional%20Amendment%2C%20the%20completion%20of%20parliamentary%20terms%2C%20and%20rival%20parties%20leading%20the%20various%20provincial%20and%20federal%20governments%20were%20all%20indicators%20of%20the%20consolidation%20of%20the%20political%20system.%20The%20PTI%20echoed%20the%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20distaste%20for%20political%20accommodation%2C%20and%20its%20charismatic%20leader%20magnified%20the%20narrative%20that%20politics%20and%20professional%20politicians%20are%20all%20about%20self-serving%20deal-making.%20He%20threatened%20to%20disrupt%20this%20system%20and%20to%20replace%20it%20with%20a%20more%20unitarian%20model%20with%20himself%20at%20the%20helm%20ably%20assisted%20by%20the%20establishment.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20political%20ambitions%20brought%20him%20into%20conflict%20with%20his%20erstwhile%20mentors%20whose%20designated%20role%20for%20him%20was%20to%20disrupt%20the%20PMLN-PPP%20compact%20but%20who%20had%20not%20thought%20things%20through%20beyond%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20establishment%20needs%20to%20hold%20Khan%20down%20because%20he%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20an%20unreliable%20interlocutor.%20It%20has%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20accept%20broader%20accommodation%20between%20the%20other%20political%20parties.%20Perhaps%20the%20most%20remarkable%20but%20unnoticed%20feature%20of%20the%20election%20results%20is%20the%20continuity%20in%20the%20popular%20mandate.%20The%20number%20of%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20main%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20notably%20PTI%2C%20PMLN%2C%20PPP%20%E2%80%93%20is%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20outcome%20in%202018.%20And%20as%20in%202018%2C%20the%20PTI%20has%20won%20a%20majority%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%2C%20the%20PPP%20in%20Sindh%2C%20while%20Punjab%20remains%20split%20down%20the%20middle.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%202024%20elections%20represent%20the%20third%20successive%20PTI%20win%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20and%20the%20fourth%20one%20for%20the%20PPP%20in%20Sindh.%20Party%20positions%20in%20national%20assembly%20seats%20from%20the%20provinces%20correspond%20closely%20with%20provincial%20assembly%20outcomes.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98national%E2%80%99%20leader%20has%20not%20dented%20the%20silent%20but%20steady%20shift%20of%20the%20centre%20of%20political%20gravity%20from%20Islamabad%20to%20the%20provincial%20capitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20results%20demonstrated%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20and%20the%20resilience%20of%20his%20party.%20But%20they%20do%20not%20change%20other%20salient%20facts.%20The%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20at%20cornering%20politicians%20through%20the%20anti-politics%20Khan%20was%20hoisted%20on%20its%20own%20petard.%20The%20failure%20of%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20attempted%20%E2%80%98insurrection%E2%80%99%20of%20May%202023%20still%20looms%20heavy%20and%20there%20will%20be%20little%20appetite%20among%20his%20supporters%20or%20the%20public%20at%20large%20for%20the%20renewal%20of%20street%20protests%20in%20Punjab.%20In%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20the%20PTI%20will%20have%20little%20reason%20to%20protest%2C%20as%20it%20is%20called%20upon%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%20sending%20its%20legislators%20and%20their%20supporters%20scrambling%20for%20office%20and%20favour.%20The%20establishment%20and%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20two%20implacable%20opponents%20of%20devolved%20and%20accommodative%20democratic%20politics%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20have%20played%20each%20other%20to%20a%20stalemate.%20Elected%20politicians%2C%20in%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20have%20their%20work%20cut%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHaris%20Gazdar%20is%20Senior%20Researcher%2C%20Collective%20for%20Social%20Science%20Research%2C%20Karachi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707627867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25140239%2FPakistan-elections.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpolitics-bounces-back-in-pakistan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20establishment%20and%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20the%20two%20implacable%20opponents%20of%20devolved%20and%20accommodative%20democratic%20politics%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20have%20played%20each%20other%20to%20a%20stalemate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpolitics-bounces-back-in-pakistan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHad%20EVMs%20Been%20There...%26quot%3B%3A%20Pakistan%20President%20Amid%20Delay%20In%20Poll%20Results%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20President%20Arif%20Alvi%20expressed%20his%20frustration%20on%20Saturday%20over%20the%20postponed%20election%20results%20and%20stated%20that%20if%20the%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20had%20been%20in%20use%20during%20the%20general%20elections%20on%20February%208%2C%20the%20nation%20would%20not%20be%20facing%20this%20current%20crisis%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20commission's%20lofty%20claims%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan's%20(ECP)%20new%20Election%20Management%20System%20(EMS)%20failed%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20election%20regulator%20has%20yet%20to%20release%20the%20preliminary%20results%20for%20every%20constituency%2C%20nearly%20seventy-two%20hours%20after%20the%20polls%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20President%20Alvi%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHad%20EVMs%20been%20there%20today%2C%20my%20dear%20beloved%20Pakistan%20would%20have%20been%20spared%20this%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Alvi%20recalled%20the%20fight%20for%20the%20EVMs%20waged%20by%20the%20previous%20PTI-led%20government%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20entire%20endeavour--which%20involved%20more%20than%2050%20meetings%20at%20the%20presidency%20alone--was%20abandoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%20'our'%20long%20struggle%20for%20EVMs.%20EVM%20had%20paper%20ballots%20that%20could%20be%20counted%20separately%20by%20hand%20(like%20it%20is%20being%20done%20today)%20but%20it%20also%20had%20a%20simple%20electronic%20calculator%2Fcounter%20of%20each%20vote%20button%20pressed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20said%20that%20the%20totals%20of%20every%20candidate%20would%20have%20been%20available%20and%20printed%20within%20five%20minutes%20of%20the%20closing%20of%20the%20poll%20if%20the%20machines%20were%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERemember%20'our'%20long%20struggle%20for%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines.%20EVM%20had%20paper%20ballots%20that%20could%20be%20counted%20separately%20by%20hand%20(like%20it%20is%20being%20done%20today)%20BUT%20it%20also%20had%20a%20simple%20electronic%20calculator%2Fcounter%20of%20each%20vote%20button%20pressed.%20Totals%20of%20every%20candidate%20would%20have%20been%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20Arif%20Alvi%20(%40ArifAlvi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FArifAlvi%2Fstatus%2F1756264268624765291%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2010%2C%20the%20Jamiat%20Ulema-e-Islam-Fazl%20(JUI-F)%20staged%20a%20protest%20over%20alleged%20rigging%20and%20alteration%20of%20results%20in%20Sindh's%20PS-22%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20%5BJUI-F's%5D%20candidate%20was%20made%20to%20lose%20via%20%5Bdeliberate%5D%20change%20of%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20JUI-F%20leader%20Rashid%20Mehmood%20Soomro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20won%20by%20%5Bmargin%20of%5D%207%2C000%20votes%20as%20per%20the%20Form%2045s%20in%20our%20possession%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20calling%20for%20fresh%2