demus%20and%20touch%20on%20%26quot%3Bmusic%2C%20food%2C%20and%20how%20to%20enjoy%20life's%20pleasures%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20post%20by%20Friedman%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20closing%20section%2C%20he%20throws%20shade%20at%20unnamed%20ideological%20adversaries%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20the%20stoics%3F%20%E2%80%94%20who%20%26quot%3Bhave%20nothing%20to%20say%20about%20pleasure%2C%20either%20in%20general%20or%20in%20particular%2C%26quot%3B%20Friedman%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETen%20months%20ago%2C%20we%20launched%20the%20Vesuvius%20Challenge%20to%20solve%20the%20ancient%20problem%20of%20the%20Herculaneum%20Papyri%2C%20a%20library%20of%20scrolls%20that%20were%20flash-fried%20by%20the%20eruption%20of%20Mount%20Vesuvius%20in%2079%20AD.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EToday%20we%20are%20overjoyed%20to%20announce%20that%20our%20crazy%20project%20has%20succeeded.%20After%202000%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ffihs9ADb48%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ffihs9ADb48%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Nat%20Friedman%20(%40natfriedman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnatfriedman%2Fstatus%2F1754519304471814555%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20competition's%20big%20winners%20helped%20uncover%20about%205%25%20of%20one%20scroll%2C%20but%20the%20competition%20doled%20out%20more%20than%2050%20prizes%20last%20year%2C%20totaling%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20to%20teams%20who%20helped%20find%20the%20first%20letters%20in%20the%20scrolls%2C%20assisted%20with%20ink%20detection%2C%20and%20developed%20open%20source%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20bar%20is%20even%20higher%2C%20