%2Fentertainment-arts-68261217%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68261217.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68261217.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajasthan%3A%20Colleges%20Hold%20Ram-Themed%20Competitions%20After%20ISRO%20Affiliated%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20Letter%20to%20CM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10170152%2FScreenshot-2024-02-10-at-5.01.28-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJaipur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Fancy%20dress%20competitions%20with%20students%20dressed%20as%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Bhakts%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Mata%20Sita%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Hanuman%20ji%E2%80%99%20along%20with%20drawing%20and%20painting%20competitions%20on%20subjects%20such%20as%20Ram%20breaking%20a%20%3Cem%3Edhanush%3C%2Fem%3E%20(bow)%20and%20Ram%2C%20Laxman%20and%20Sita%20touring%20the%20forest%20are%20some%20of%20the%20themes%20for%20the%20two-day%20long%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Antariksh%20Vedshala%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20an%20event%20being%20organised%20by%20the%20India%20Space%20Week%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20celebrated%20in%20schools%20and%20educational%20institutions%20of%20Rajasthan%20on%20February%209%20and%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20circular%20dated%20February%208%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20College%20Education%2C%20Rajasthan%20government%20has%20directed%20principals%20of%20all%20government%20colleges%20in%20the%20state%20to%20ensure%20the%20compliance%20of%20another%20letter%20written%20in%20January%20by%20the%20India%20Space%20Week%20to%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%20about%20organising%20Ram%20Antariksh%20Vedshala.%20The%20letter%20mentions%20the%20aforementioned%20activities%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Vedshala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1I302X0wDVAYNUmnRcEwgxBt1Lc1IRCaN%2Fpreview%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20website%2C%20the%20India%20Space%20Week%20is%20an%20approved%20nodal%20institute%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Remote%20Sensing%20(IIRS)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20unit%20of%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20outreach%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20dated%20January%2018%2C%20the%20India%20Space%20Week%20had%20written%20to%20Rajasthan%20chief%20minister%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20communicating%20its%20plans%20of%20organising%20various%20programmes%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Ram%20Antariksh%20Vedshala%20in%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20universities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20letter%2C%20which%20has%20been%20attached%20and%20cited%20in%20the%20February%208%20circular%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20College%20Education%2C%20the%20students%20are%20expected%20to%20participate%20in%20fancy%20dress%20competitions%20themed%20on%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20themes%20for%20the%20fancy%20dress%20competition%20include%20dressing%20up%20as%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Bhakts%E2%80%99%20and%20enact%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%3B%20as%20Sita%20and%20enact%20planting%20trees%20at%20Ashok%20Vatika%3B%20as%20Hanuman%20and%20enact%20Hanuman%20carrying%20the%20Sanjeevani%20Parvat%20and%20dressing%20up%20as%20Ram%2C%20Laxman%2C%20Hanuman%20and%20Ravan%20with%20Ram%20honouring%20the%20best%20qualities%20of%20his%20enemies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20drawing%20and%20painting%20competition%20has%20five%20themes%20%E2%80%93%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20Sita%20watering%20trees%2C%20Ram%20breaking%20a%20bow%2C%20Ram%2C%20Laxman%2C%20Sita%20touring%20a%20forest%20and%20Hanuman%20and%20the%20Vanar%20Sena%20building%20the%20Ram%20Setu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%2C%20India%20will%20enter%20a%20new%20era.%20One%20has%20to%20apply%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20principles%20in%20life%20and%20make%20oneself%20Rammay%20and%20Prakriti%20may%20(favourable%20towards%20nature).%20Ram%20Rajya%20was%20a%20very%20rich%20and%20a%20golden%20age%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20environment.%20Ram%20Rajya%20was%20filled%20with%20forest%20lands.%20All%20trees%20were%20green%2C%20and%20were%20full%20of%20flowers%20and%20fruits.%20This%20tradition%20tells%20us%20all%20that%20nature%20is%20the%20bedrock%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20letter%2C%20written%20in%20Hindi%2C%20by%20the%20India%20Space%20Week%20to%20Sharma%20days%20before%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20adds%20that%20thousands%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20Ram%20had%20stayed%20amidst%20nature%20and%20that%20people%20draw%20inspiration%20to%20save%20environment%20from%20his%2014%20years%20of%20%E2%80%98vanvas%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20circular%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Department%20of%20College%20Education%20has%20urged%20all%20government%20college%20principals%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20letter%20of%20the%20India%20Space%20Week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707565890000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10170152%2FScreenshot-2024-02-10-at-5.01.28-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frajasthan-colleges-hold-ram-themed-competitions-after-isro-affiliated-organisations-letter-to-cm%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20its%20circular%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Department%20of%20College%20Education%20has%20urged%20all%20government%20college%20principals%20to%20comply%20with%20India%20Space%20Week's%20letter%20asking%20for%20Ram-themed%20competitions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frajasthan-colleges-hold-ram-themed-competitions-after-isro-affiliated-org