%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10152841%2Funnamed-3.jpg%20424w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10152841%2Funnamed-3-276x300.jpg%20276w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696513%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EImage%3A%20Ashoka%20Archives%20of%20Contemporary%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20elaborated%20to%20his%20friend%20Ammu%20Joseph%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommunalism%20was%20the%20one%20issue%20which%20made%20me%20feel%20that%20if%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20actively%20fight%20it%20I%20would%20still%20be%20making%20a%20political%20statement.%20I%20felt%20I%20had%20to%20take%20a%20stand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spectacle%20of%20destruction%2C%20impunity%2C%20and%20political%20cynicism%20that%20had%20unfolded%20in%20Ayodhya%20demanded%20a%20response%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20from%20Karnad%20but%20also%20from%20his%20circle%20of%20friends%20and%20other%20artists.%20The%20Coalition%20for%20Secularism%2C%20a%20voluntary%20collective%2C%20came%20together%20in%20Bangalore%20to%20help%20people%20speak%20up%20and%20organise%20against%20this%20cult%20of%20violent%20and%20weaponised%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20forefront%20of%20artists%E2%80%99%20protests%20and%20solidarity%20was%20the%20Safdar%20Hashmi%20Memorial%20Trust%2C%20or%20SAHMAT.%20The%20Trust%20held%20events%20throughout%20the%20year%20of%201993%3B%20their%20climax%20took%20place%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20Independence%20Day%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2015%2C%201993%2C%20several%20hundreds%20of%20artists%2C%20writers%2C%20scholars%20and%20organisers%20gathered%20in%20Ayodhya%20to%20reclaim%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20heritage%20from%20hatred.%20On%20the%20Ram-ki-Paidi%20ghat%20along%20the%20Sarayu%20River%2C%20they%20held%20an%20all-night%20performance%20of%20music%20and%20dance%2C%20Muktnaad.%20Legendary%20performers%20such%20as%20Sitara%20Devi%2C%20K