%20with%20various%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Satyam%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20R-SAM-PRO%20is%20based%20on%20a%20microprocessor.%20It%20has%20a%20set%20of%20sensors%20for%20TDS%20(total%20dissolved%20solids)%2C%20turbidity%2C%20dissolved%20oxygen%2C%20GPS%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20pressure%2C%20alongside%20an%20additional%20sensor%20for%20component%20area%20humidity%20monitoring.%20Upon%20activation%2C%20these%20sensors%20relay%20data%20to%20the%20microprocessor%2C%20which%20processes%20and%20securely%20transmits%20it%20to%20a%20real-time%20database.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20access%20this%20data%20through%20a%20user-friendly%20console%2C%20visualising%20it%20in%20graphical%20or%20tabular%20formats%20and%20tracking%20the%20sensor%E2%80%99s%20location.%20The%20device%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Chybrid%20power%20management%20system%E2%80%9D%20ensures%20its%20operational%20longevity%20across%20day%20and%20night%20cycles%2C%20making%20it%20versatile%20for%20various%20applications%2C%20from%20municipal%20water%20monitoring%20to%20industrial%20wastewater%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20work%20is%20protected%20by%20a%20patent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20further%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20device%20leverages%20the%20IoT%20for%20seamless%20communication%20between%20devices%20and%20cloud-based%20databases%2C%20significantly%20enhancing%20its%20utility%20and%20accessibility.%20The%20vast%20data%20collected%20can%20be%20used%20to%20train%20AI%20models%20to%20predict%20water%20quality%20variations%2C%20providing%20valuable%20insights%20for%20both%20local%20populations%20and%20industrial%20settings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20IoT%20and%20AI%20technologies%20advance%2C%20they%20promise%20to%20revolutionise%20our%20understanding%20and%20management%20of%20water%20resources%20and%20sanitation.%20For%20example%2C%20ba