her%20children%20modelled%20her%20behaviour.%20Soon%2C%20Moushmi%20started%20following%20her%20passions%2C%20which%20included%20biking%20and%20trekking.%20She%20bought%20a%20bike%20for%20herself%20in%202013%20and%20started%20going%20on%20long%20solo%20rides.%20She%20also%20started%20her%20own%20venture%2C%20an%20event%20decor%20company%2C%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20professional%20photographer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBiking%20gives%20me%20a%20sense%20of%20freedom.%20It%20feels%20meditative%20and%20makes%20me%20feel%20independent.%20Travelling%20gives%20me%20a%20different%20perspective%20on%20life.%20I%20also%20started%20challenging%20my%20limitations%20by%20trekking.%20Every%20trek%20feels%20like%20an%20attempt%20to%20conquer%20our%20physical%20and%20mental%20obstacles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoushmi%20had%20support%20from%20her%20in-laws%20as%20she%20embarked%20on%20these%20trips.%20Her%20children%2C%20too%2C%20learnt%20to%20be%20independent.%20Vedansh%20also%20started%20attending%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20helped%20me%20give%20my%20kids%20direction%20and%20motivate%20them.%20Both%20my%20kids%20are%20not%20dependent%20on%20me%20now.%20Vedansh%20takes%20care%20of%20himself%20with%20his%20limitations%20and%20capabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20one%20night%20biking%20trips%2C%20Moushmi%20decided%20that%20it%20was%20time%20to%20go%20on%20her%20dream%C2%A0ride%20to%20Ladakh.%20Initially%2C%20she%20admits%20to%20being%20scared%20as%20she%20was%20a%20new%20rider%20and%20this%20would%20be%20her%20first%20long%20distance%20trip.%20But%20having%20crossed%20the%20age%20of%2035%20at%20that%20time%2C%20she%20decided%20that%20it%20was%20now%20or%20never.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20have%20a%20worry%20at%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20something%20were%20to%20happen%20to%20me.%20What%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20decision%20I%20to