ons%3A%20Lion%20King%20Rock%2C%20a%20one-hour%20hike%3B%20Lamaduk%2C%20a%20four-hour%20trek%3B%20and%20Rani%20Su%20Lake%2C%20a%20full-day%20hike.%20Guests%20can%20enjoy%20these%20excursions%20at%20an%20additional%20cost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20these%20treks%2C%20Heena%20makes%20sure%20there%20is%20no%20plastic%20waste%20discarded%20by%20her%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20maintain%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20hills.%20On%20my%20way%20back%2C%20we%20also%20collect%20the%20garbage%20we%20find%20on%20the%20path%20to%20keep%20the%20surroundings%20clean%20and%20green%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUmang%20Thebaria%2C%20who%20visited%20Afsana%20Homestay%2C%20has%20some%20wonderful%20things%20to%20share%20about%20his%20stay.%20%E2%80%9COne%20word%20that%20sums%20up%20my%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20home.%20It%20was%20so%20cosy%20and%20home-like%20that%20we%20decided%20to%20miss%20our%20bus%20only%20to%20stay%20a%20few%20more%20hours%20on%20the%20balcony%20and%20soak%20in%20the%20silence.%20The%20delicious%20meals%20that%20Ludramani%20Bhai%20Ji%20made%20for%20us%20were%20so%20simple%20yet%20delicious%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolitude%20is%20something%20that%20helps%20you%20find%20yourself%20and%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20I%20felt%20in%20the%20property.%20I%20can%20not%20go%20to%20Manali%20without%20visiting%20Afsana%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Heena%20says%20that%20the%20serenity%20around%20the%20homestay%20makes%20her%20guests%20forget%20all%20worries%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC13v_MgyMkR%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC13v_MgyMkR%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dlo