rations%20of%20mothers%20were%20facing%20the%20same%20problem%2C%20and%20now%20Ahana%20knew%20what%20her%20business%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20an%20innovation%20hub%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20there%20was%20no%20one%20solving%20the%20problem%20of%20making%20healthier%20biscuits%2C%20cookies%20and%20chips.%20Moms%20still%20had%20to%20give%20their%20children%20maida%20biscuits%20and%20deep-fried%20snacks.%20My%20sister-in-law%20had%20the%20same%20options%20from%20the%20same%20brands%20as%20my%20mother%20did%2C%20almost%2030%20years%20ago!%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20offer%20improved%20products%20to%20families%20and%20working%20professionals%2C%20she%20came%20back%20to%20Mumbai%20in%202018.%20She%20began%20conducting%20surveys%20to%20understand%20people%E2%80%99s%20food%20preferences%20and%20what%20factors%20would%20make%20them%20trust%20a%20new%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20said%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20eat%20healthy%2C%20but%20no%20one%20wanted%20to%20compromise%20on%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20now%20Mumbai%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201210px)%20100vw%2C%201210px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221210%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20packing%20Open%20Secret%20products%20at%20their%20factory%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295.jpeg%201210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-300x162.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-500x270.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-768x415.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen1-1706874295-