20visited%20customers%20in%20metro%20cities%2C%20gaining%20valuable%20insights%20into%20their%20snacking%20preferences.%20Drawing%20on%20this%20knowledge%2C%20she%20conducted%20focus%20groups%20to%20identify%20customer%20favourites%20in%20snacks%2C%20cookies%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20focus%20groups%2C%20we%20asked%20people%20what%20they%20liked%20and%20disliked%20in%20the%20snacks%20they%20were%20eating.%20The%20uniform%20response%20from%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20working%20professionals%2C%20students%20or%20moms%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20maida.%20I%20then%20asked%20them%20what%20they%20found%20healthy%2C%20to%20which%20most%20said%20dry%20fruits%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20this%20feedback%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20an%20in-house%20R%26amp%3BD%20team%2C%20Ahana%20worked%20on%20formulating%20the%20perfect%20%E2%80%98unjunked%E2%80%99%20cookie.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20unjunked%20the%20typical%20cookie%20by%20replacing%20maida%20with%2040%20to%2050%20percent%20dry%20fruits%20and%20millet%20using%20less%20sugar.%20Most%20of%20our%20products%20have%20just%201%20to%202%20grams%20of%20sugar%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20involved%20a%20group%20of%20100%20mothers%2C%20dubbed%20by%20Ahana%20as%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Chief%20Innovation%20Officers%E2%80%99.%20Ahana%20sent%20them%20various%20flavours%20and%20samples%2C%20using%20their%20feedback%20to%20improve%20the%20products.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20helped%20us%20crack%20the%20right%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20asserts%20that%20they%20have%20taken%20measures%20to%20guarantee%20the%20snacks%20remain%20delectable%20even%20after%20substituting%20certain%20ingredients%20with%20their%20nutritious%20counterparts.%20This%20ensures%20that%20customers%20not%20only%20enjoy%20the%20taste%20but%20also%20reap%20health%20benefits%20from%20their%20consumption.%20Hence%2C%20nine%20months%20and%201%2C000%20cookies%20later%2C%20Ahana%20was%20ready%20with%20the%20first%20product%20%E2%80%94%20the%20nutty%20cookie%2C%20which%20to%20date%20is%20their%20bestseller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20challenge%20was%20learning%20how%20to%20manufacture%20the%20product.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20product%20with%20no%20benchmark.%20I%20had%20to%20use%20my%20engineering%20skills%20to%20set%20up%20the%20right%20assembly%20line.%20We%20also%20had%20to%20work%20on%20extending%20the%20shelf%20life%20without%20adding%20preservatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20uses%20aluminium%20in%20the%20packaging%20to%20extend%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20her%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20finally%20launched%20%E2%80%98Open%20Secret%E2%80%99%20in%20January%202020%20through%20online%20and%20offline%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Open%20Secret%20has%20over%2030%20categories%20of%20products%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981.jpeg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-02-at-01.43.20-1-1707133981-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.th