80%9CI%20thoroughly%20examine%20every%20aspect%20%E2%80%94%20scrutinising%20the%20hotel%2C%20the%20country%20itself%2C%20and%20its%20wheelchair%20accessibility.%20It%E2%80%99s%20essential%20to%20call%20the%20hotel%20or%20homestay%20in%20advance%20to%20confirm%20if%20they%20are%20fully%20equipped%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20a%20wheelchair%20user.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20time%20like%20the%20present%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20such%20inspiring%20traveller%20who%20is%20on%20a%20unique%20mission%20to%20navigate%20the%20Ganga%20River%20in%20100%20days!%20A%20patient%20with%20rheumatoid%20arthritis%20with%20very%20little%20mobility%20in%20his%20fingers%20and%20left%20leg%2C%20Rency%20Thomas%20feels%20a%20sense%20of%20urgency%20with%20his%20condition%20and%20advises%20not%20to%20hesitate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20easy%20for%20people%20facing%20similar%20conditions%20like%20mine%20to%20lose%20heart%20and%20stop%20living.%20But%20I%20want%20to%20convey%20that%20it%20is%20possible.%20Whatever%20you%E2%80%99re%20dreaming%2C%20if%20you%20push%20yourself%20enough%2C%20you%20can%20achieve%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20good%20team%20to%20back%20you%20up%20in%20such%20expeditions%20is%20the%20key%20to%20success.%20%E2%80%9CNavigating%20the%20high%20tidal%20river%20can%20be%20hard%20but%20my%20team%20has%20my%20back%20and%20is%20prepared%20for%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGo%20solo%20but%20be%20safe%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20patient%20of%20epilepsy%2C%20travelling%20for%20Priti%20Vishwakarma%20was%20always%20a%20far-fetched%20dream.%20However%2C%20the%20comments%20of%20society%20and%20her%20health%20could%20prevent%20her%20from%20achieving%20her%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEpileptic%20patients%20often%20find%20themselves%20confined%20